-- Meeting: Powerhouse Gym & Ideometry: Weekly Sync (2025-11-05 16:00:00+00)
WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    'e7336694-2c40-4fcf-a7ef-4d0460f053c8',
    '2025-11-05 16:00:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01K8RB8XGTN1JP7J2CV9DWB169',
    'Powerhouse Gym & Ideometry: Weekly Sync',
    '{"Nina Belina","Colin Costigan","Milan Wagner","Yefei Jin"}'::text[],
    2657,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86061042503?pwd=x0TBEgRs7qFmrRIEItauCzbH71kaq8.1',
    '{"id":"01K8RB8XGTN1JP7J2CV9DWB169","title":"Powerhouse Gym & Ideometry: Weekly Sync","summary":{"notes":"## **HubSpot System Stabilization and Workflow Optimization**\n\nThe team agreed that the core HubSpot system is nearing stability, with ongoing fixes focused on workflow overlaps and lead management (07:44).\n\n- **Nina Belina reported resolving parallel workflow conflicts in HubSpot** by staggering start times, preventing contacts from being manually removed from lists (07:44)\n    - This fix ensures contacts now appear correctly in both the hot and club visited lists without overlap.\n    - Milan Wagner confirmed that sales added a \"last activity\" or \"last engagement\" date column to track contact interactions more accurately.\n    - Nina clarified that HubSpot can only track context and activity going forward, not retroactively.\n    - This update reduces daily system errors and improves lead tracking accuracy.\n\n- **Milan Wagner and Yefei Jin agreed that HubSpot work remains the priority for this month**, reserving a **bucket of about 10 hours** monthly for ongoing HubSpot support and tweaks (19:30)\n    - Colin Costigan confirmed **24 hours remain for this month’s work**, refreshed with a new purchase of **29 hours** at the start of the month (09:56).\n    - The team expects HubSpot issues to taper off as workflows mature, aiming to avoid core fixes extending into December.\n    - Yefei emphasized the need for early issue reporting to prevent prolonged workflow problems.\n    - Milan noted that recent fixes on lead sources and contact methods have addressed most core HubSpot priorities (24:31).\n\n- **Marketing drip campaigns are active and being validated for effectiveness**, with particular attention to Facebook meta leads and re-enrolling reinquired contacts (25:17)\n    - Milan shared that the lead drip campaign has delivered emails to **1,022 leads** over two months and confirmed re-enrollment for repeat inquires will be turned back on.\n    - Colin clarified that meta lead counts from HubSpot closely match form submissions, with minor differences due to reinquiries.\n    - The team agreed all website form leads funnel through HubSpot workflows.\n    - Ensuring drip campaigns reach all appropriate leads remains a key performance metric.\n\n## **SMS Marketing Integration and Platform Evaluation**\n\nThe group is weighing options between HubSpot’s SMS marketing feature and Aircall’s third-party SMS platform, balancing cost and functionality (31:20).\n\n- **HubSpot SMS marketing was favored for initial rollout due to lower costs and easier automation setup**, with estimated additional costs around **$600** (39:38)\n    - Milan reported Aircall’s SMS platform costs approximately **$1,100 total** including per-message fees, nearly double HubSpot’s price (39:43).\n    - HubSpot supports automated SMS triggered by lead status or form submissions, facilitating marketing workflows.\n    - Milan is tasked with clarifying integration and trigger details between HubSpot, Aircall, and third-party SMS tools.\n    - Yefei emphasized the value of starting with the cheaper HubSpot option for quicker setup and troubleshooting.\n\n- **SMS marketing use cases include automated notifications for offers, first inquiries, and missed appointments**, enhancing engagement (32:26)\n    - Responses to SMS messages would notify contact owners via email for follow-up through Aircall or HubSpot.\n    - HubSpot would consolidate SMS replies into lead lists, while Aircall offers two-way texting within reps’ personal SMS platforms.\n    - Milan has a scheduled call with a HubSpot rep to gather more technical details and pricing clarifications (39:16).\n    - The team plans to test SMS flows and train Milan on editing and running campaigns to enable agile mid-month adjustments.\n\n## **Website Development Strategy and Resource Allocation**\n\nThe team is balancing ongoing small fixes on the current Squarespace site against a potential larger WordPress redesign, mindful of resource constraints (09:39).\n\n- **Colin explained that the current monthly hours (around 25) are mostly allocated between HubSpot and Squarespace facelift work**, limiting capacity for a full WordPress rebuild without additional contracts (10:18)\n    - The option to start a WordPress redesign was discussed but would consume hours rapidly, leaving no time for HubSpot improvements.\n    - Yefei suggested continuing small UI fixes on Squarespace for now, emphasizing planning for a future larger site build with e-commerce and POS integration.\n    - Colin noted Shopify integration could be added as a simple button in Squarespace or as a dedicated page in a new WordPress site.\n    - The team is deferring any major website overhaul until a comprehensive cost and timeline comparison is completed.\n\n- **The team confirmed that unused hours roll over fully, with no partial hour forfeiture**, ensuring efficient use of purchased time (18:18)\n    - Colin detailed **188 total hours purchased historically**, with about **180 hours delivered so far**, and a current credit of **22.25 hours** available (19:10).\n    - This rollover enables flexibility during months with fluctuating workload demands.\n    - Yefei emphasized the need to keep the current system stable before engaging in major website projects.\n    - Milan agreed to monitor daily issues to help draw a clear line for system stability.\n\n## **Data Track Integration and Documentation Preparation**\n\nThe team is preparing detailed documentation for a third party building a new POS system to replace Data Track, clarifying integration points and system rationale (04:21).\n\n- **Yefei Jin and Milan Wagner are leading efforts to add context on Data Track’s key features and integration with HubSpot and Aircall**, aiming for delivery by Thursday (11:11)\n    - Milan will add a new section summarizing Data Track’s **top five features**, focusing on sales processing and member check-in functions.\n    - They will document why the team switched from Salesforce and Rank DNA to HubSpot and Aircall, highlighting cost and functionality benefits.\n    - The document will outline the reasons for separating syncs (member status, transactions) and the cost/complexity of each (05:22).\n    - Yefei stressed including in-scope and planned features like e-signature workflows, noting PandaDoc is a temporary workaround.\n\n- **The document will provide a high-level overview first, with technical screenshots and details available upon follow-up requests**, managing client expectations (16:54)\n    - Colin suggested providing screenshots from Make.com to show workflow complexity without overwhelming on initial calls.\n    - Yefei expects Motion IQ to lead the initial meeting and ask questions to clarify integration needs.\n    - The team will prepare to explain the rationale behind multiple syncs and the potential need for APIs.\n    - This approach supports transparent vendor collaboration and informed POS system design.\n\n## **Operational Process Improvements and Team Collaboration**\n\nThe team is focused on refining daily workflows and communication protocols to speed issue resolution and improve system reliability (20:12).\n\n- **Yefei highlighted the need for rapid reporting of issues by gym staff to avoid delays in fixes**, aiming to eliminate core system bugs by December (23:50)\n    - Milan acknowledged that while some occasional breaks occur, the majority of workflows are stable.\n    - Nina clarified that some recent issues stemmed from adding workflows not originally designed for multiple parallel processes.\n    - The team agreed that new feature requests are expected after core stability is reached.\n    - Yefei proposed a goal of one full week without system breakage or urgent questions to mark stability (38:28).\n\n- **Colin and Yefei plan to assist Milan with HubSpot workflow management training**, enabling more autonomous control of marketing lists and campaign adjustments (40:11)\n    - Milan has started exploring HubSpot’s flow pages but has not yet made changes.\n    - Colin assured that workflow editing is straightforward once the necessary contact properties and triggers are understood.\n    - This training will reduce dependency on external support and allow faster mid-month campaign tweaks.\n    - The team will continue collaborating closely on HubSpot and Squarespace tasks to maintain progress.\n\n","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot","SMS Marketing","Data Track","POS System","Workflows","Website Facelift"],"overview":"- **HubSpot Workflow Stabilization:** Core HubSpot system is stabilizing with ongoing fixes for workflow overlaps and lead management. \n\n- **HubSpot Work Priority:** Ongoing HubSpot support remains priority; 10 hours monthly reserved for tweaks and adjustments.\n\n- **Marketing Drip Campaign Progress:** Active drip campaigns have emailed 1,022 leads; re-enrollment for repeat inquiries will resume.\n\n- **SMS Marketing Cost Comparison:** HubSpot SMS feature favored due to lower estimated costs of $600 vs. Aircall’s $1,100.\n\n- **Website Development Plan:** Current site fixes continue while larger WordPress redesign awaits cost and timeline comparison.\n\n- **Data Track Documentation Preparation:** Team documenting Data Track''s features and integration rationale for new POS systems delivery by Thursday.","action_items":"\n**Milan Wagner**\nReview and contribute to the document detailing backend workflows for the POS system rebuild (05:54)\nAdd a section summarizing Data Track key features and issues resolved with HubSpot (14:56)\nAttend the HubSpot rep call, compile detailed questions about SMS integration and platform limitations, and report back (39:16)\nCoordinate with Colin and Nina on HubSpot issues promptly as they arise (43:42)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nAssist in updating the backend workflows document for synchronization scenarios and costs, including screenshots of the make.com system (11:19)\nProvide support for SMS marketing setup, create necessary workflows, and teach Milan how to manage HubSpot flows (40:08)\nDeliver the finalized critical workflows document to Milan and Yefei for onward submission by tomorrow (43:42)\nContinue working on the Squarespace facelift project within current monthly hours (43:42)\n\n**Nina Belina**\nSupport HubSpot workflow troubleshooting and ensure fixes prevent contact list overlaps (07:24)\nProvide technical explanations and collaborate to maintain system stability (20:41)\n\n**Yefei Jin**\nCoordinate the integration of the critical workflows document and oversee communication with Motion IQ (11:19)\nLead discussions on budget allocation for monthly hours, prioritizing HubSpot and SMS implementation within current resources (18:18)\nAdvise on SMS platform evaluation and ensure questions for HubSpot rep are clear and thorough (35:35)\nFacilitate prioritization to reach stable HubSpot system operations and reduce daily issues by end of the month (38:25)\nSupport decision-making on future website redesign projects and budgeting for online store integration (37:18)\n"},"duration":44.290000915527344,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Nina Belina"},{"id":1,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":2,"name":"Milan Wagner"},{"id":3,"name":"Yefei Jin"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":206.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":205.84,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Hey, how''s it going?","index":1,"end_time":207.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":206.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Did you see my message?","index":2,"end_time":209.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":208,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":3,"end_time":212.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":211.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The other option is we can see if another designer can help out.","index":4,"end_time":216.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":213.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because I know that now, like they have a browser version so you can just log in and.","index":5,"end_time":224.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":220.72,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"No, well, I''ve been.","index":6,"end_time":229.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":228.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, no parties.","index":7,"end_time":234.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":229.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, none of that.","index":8,"end_time":234.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":234.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I. I''ve been.","index":9,"end_time":236.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":234.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve been hanging out with my family.","index":10,"end_time":242.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":239.69,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, hello.","index":11,"end_time":255.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":245.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Can you guys hear me?","index":12,"end_time":256.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":255.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Ken, what''s up?","index":13,"end_time":259.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":256.98,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How we doing?","index":14,"end_time":259.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":259.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How''s it going?","index":15,"end_time":260.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":259.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good.","index":16,"end_time":261.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":261.54,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Cannot complain.","index":17,"end_time":263.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":262.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Cannot complain.","index":18,"end_time":266.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":265.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, let''s chat about these.","index":19,"end_time":269.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":268.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t think anybody else is gonna be joining us.","index":20,"end_time":272.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":269.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Let''s chat about this meeting on Friday.","index":21,"end_time":275.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":272.98,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Colin.","index":22,"end_time":276.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":276.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, so basically these guys are coming in and they''re trying to rebuild like this POS system, which is going to be like the equivalent for data track.","index":23,"end_time":287.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":276.98,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And I think that they want to know the back end stuff of like what we''ve had to do on make and the work that we''ve had to do to get things working on HubSpot.","index":24,"end_time":299.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":287.98,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then also the reason why we switched from Salesforce and Rank DNA to HubSpot and Aircall.","index":25,"end_time":307.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":301.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":26,"end_time":309.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":309.07,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Which I feel like has the answer for that one mainly.","index":27,"end_time":318.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":312.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But yeah, yeah, I can even pull.","index":28,"end_time":322.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":318.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Up the document that he created.","index":29,"end_time":323.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":322.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it looks like he just needs us to fill in this section.","index":30,"end_time":331.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":329.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Member sync.","index":31,"end_time":335.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":334.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Member that is Sync.","index":32,"end_time":338.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":335.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":33,"end_time":339.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":338.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Just what these scenarios do and our cost.","index":34,"end_time":343.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":340.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, let me just see if he added me into.","index":35,"end_time":350.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":344.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Am I added to that one as well or.","index":36,"end_time":352.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":350.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It was a different one.","index":37,"end_time":353.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":352.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"This is.","index":38,"end_time":354.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":354.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Anyone with a link?","index":39,"end_time":355.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":354.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, but he like tagged just YouTube.","index":40,"end_time":359.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":357.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think he requested me to add some stuff myself.","index":41,"end_time":363.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":360.98,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Guess she only tagged you guys on that, right?","index":42,"end_time":367.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":364.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, he said can you contribute all.","index":43,"end_time":369.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":367.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"He said he tagged you and said can you contribute to it?","index":44,"end_time":371.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":369.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, Nice and big.","index":45,"end_time":376.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":372.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll figure it out.","index":46,"end_time":381.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":380.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":47,"end_time":381.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":381.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you need me for the member sync, member status sync and transaction sync or you guys got that?","index":48,"end_time":389.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":384.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, I feel like.","index":49,"end_time":391.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":390.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sorry, go ahead.","index":50,"end_time":393.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":392.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Was that Michael?","index":51,"end_time":395.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":394.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Who''s doing that?","index":52,"end_time":395.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":395.04,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Michael originally built all of that and then we had to go through and update quite a bit of it.","index":53,"end_time":400.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":396.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, okay, cool.","index":54,"end_time":406.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":401.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well then I''ll let you guys do that.","index":55,"end_time":407.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":406.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":56,"end_time":408.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":408.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Are you still contracted with Michael or is this.","index":57,"end_time":411.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":409.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, I think we.","index":58,"end_time":413.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":412.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, I don''t know if.","index":59,"end_time":415.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":414,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t know if ek, like officially like ended it, but we''re trying not to use them.","index":60,"end_time":421.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":415.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Incredibly expensive apparently.","index":61,"end_time":423.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":422.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":62,"end_time":424.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":424.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, we can, you know, we can work with the developers to get this information added in.","index":63,"end_time":430.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":425.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool, cool.","index":64,"end_time":435.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":432.96,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What''s been going on with HubSpot guys?","index":65,"end_time":437.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":435.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You guys are killing Me, every morning I get a heart attack.","index":66,"end_time":440.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":437.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Heart attack every morning.","index":67,"end_time":445.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":444.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It looks good now, but the last two days I was.","index":68,"end_time":450.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":446.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I was having a heart attack.","index":69,"end_time":452.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":451.29,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":70,"end_time":454.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Nina, do you want to speak to some of the stuff that was going.","index":71,"end_time":457.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":454.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was in a leadership meeting Monday at Milan, so I was out of the office completely.","index":72,"end_time":461.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":457.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, you''re good.","index":73,"end_time":463.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":462.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You''re good.","index":74,"end_time":463.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":463.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we had a lot of, I mean, not a lot of, but a few fixes because we added workflow for reconnecting customers.","index":75,"end_time":473.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":464.89,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And then for HubSpot, for example, if you have a couple of workflows that are working at the same time, sometimes it can happen that, for example, HubSpot overrides some contacts as manual, like manually takes them out of the list if they see that there''s two workflows working at the same time.","index":76,"end_time":495.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":473.38,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So now we fixed it so it doesn''t overlap.","index":77,"end_time":498.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":495.94,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So one workflow is still starting a little bit later than the others, so it doesn''t actually work in parallel.","index":78,"end_time":504.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":498.62,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But that was mostly what was happening with the HubSpot list.","index":79,"end_time":509.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":505.03,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Everything else should be working fine, especially if the sales people added that column for a last activity.","index":80,"end_time":515.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":509.23,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So we know that.","index":81,"end_time":517.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":516.47,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, they did.","index":82,"end_time":519.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":517.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":83,"end_time":520.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":519.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Appreciate you, Nina.","index":84,"end_time":521.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":520.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":85,"end_time":522.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":521.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I know that I was bombarding you with messages, so I appreciate you working fast with this too.","index":86,"end_time":528.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":522.39,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, they have added that, like last activity date as well.","index":87,"end_time":536.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":531.14,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s not the exact word for it.","index":88,"end_time":538.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":536.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Or last engagement date.","index":89,"end_time":539.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":538.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And also remember that, like, it can only add contexts in the future and not retroactively.","index":90,"end_time":547.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":540.18,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So unfortunately you cannot see, you know, previous attempts.","index":91,"end_time":551.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":547.38,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So.","index":92,"end_time":552.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":551.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":93,"end_time":552.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":552.53,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, then moving forward, it should all be working correctly.","index":94,"end_time":558.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":554.53,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, that sounds good.","index":95,"end_time":561.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":560.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s fine.","index":96,"end_time":563.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":563.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Then with HubSpot, I don''t really have too many questions or concerns with some of the stuff.","index":97,"end_time":569.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":563.61,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If I do, I''ll reach out to you guys on the Slack channel.","index":98,"end_time":574.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":569.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"In terms of the website, has there been any, like, progress there?","index":99,"end_time":578.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":574.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":100,"end_time":580.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":579.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you want to chat through some of the ideas that we had there?","index":101,"end_time":582.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":580.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One thing I will say, Milan, is we are at negative 13 hours as the.","index":102,"end_time":590.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":583.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"As you guys just got re upped at the beginning of the month with another 29 purchase.","index":103,"end_time":594.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":590.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, wait, no.","index":104,"end_time":595.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":594.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, hold on.","index":105,"end_time":596.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":595.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It just bounced back up.","index":106,"end_time":597.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":596.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so we''re good.","index":107,"end_time":598.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":597.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, what are we at now?","index":108,"end_time":602.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":600.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We''re at 24.","index":109,"end_time":604.201,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":602.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"24 total hours.","index":110,"end_time":606.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":604.419,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":111,"end_time":606.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":606.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For the month available.","index":112,"end_time":607.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":606.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And you don''t lose any hours.","index":113,"end_time":612.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":611.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like we don''t do like the half hour rollover thing anymore.","index":114,"end_time":616.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":612.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":115,"end_time":619.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":618.96,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So, yeah, what we were chatting through and Nina, feel free to cut me off at any point was obviously Giving the facelift to Squarespace, but also working.","index":116,"end_time":626.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":619.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We talked about maybe going in tandem with starting a WordPress website design project, but that would burn through these hours very quickly and we would have no time to work on HubSpot, which I know we definitely need to save a bucket for.","index":117,"end_time":638.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":627.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so I wanted to chat with you or maybe if, if we chat with Yifei about it, like a, maybe a project retainer for a website build.","index":118,"end_time":647.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":639.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, well, Yifei just joined on for the call, so.","index":119,"end_time":652.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":649.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, perfect timing.","index":120,"end_time":654.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":652.27,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Hey.","index":121,"end_time":655.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":654.59,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Hey, Yifei.","index":122,"end_time":656.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":655.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey.","index":123,"end_time":657.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":657.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What''s going on?","index":124,"end_time":657.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":657.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What are we talking about?","index":125,"end_time":659.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":658.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we went through the document that you shared, so our team''s gonna go through that and update the section that you tagged me and Nina in.","index":126,"end_time":666.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":659.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Was there anything else specifically you wanted to call out in that document?","index":127,"end_time":670.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":667.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t know what you''re like, the level of detail.","index":128,"end_time":674.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":671.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, do you think you could get to it as well if you haven''t already?","index":129,"end_time":679.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":674.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I haven''t done so yet, but.","index":130,"end_time":681.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":679.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But I''m gonna review it after this.","index":131,"end_time":683.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":681.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":132,"end_time":684.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":683.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, this group, the, the context is, is like, I think we''ll have them, we''ll.","index":133,"end_time":691.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":685.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I want to send this to them, like ideally today''s Wednesday, like I guess tomorrow is fine.","index":134,"end_time":698.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":691.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So they can review it.","index":135,"end_time":701.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":700.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then I think I''ll just have them facilitate the meeting.","index":136,"end_time":706.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":701.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They''ll probably have questions for us like, how does this work?","index":137,"end_time":709.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":706.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How does that work?","index":138,"end_time":710,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":709.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then let''s just be prepared to do some screen share, either HubSpot or make.","index":139,"end_time":715.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":710.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It may not get there, it may not become that technical, but I''m going to let them lead it.","index":140,"end_time":723.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":717.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know how they''re going to facilitate it.","index":141,"end_time":724.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":723.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, it''d be interesting if they wanted to dive into like tactical specifications on a first call rather than like a high level overview of how these things connect.","index":142,"end_time":732.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":725.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But we''ll be prepared for both.","index":143,"end_time":734.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":733.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I think it might be good to like here to.","index":144,"end_time":740.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":735.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You can probably just screenshot some of the make stuff so that they have a sense of like what the level of complexity that this is and you can just.","index":145,"end_time":754.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":742.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''ll share, share like the document with them so you don''t even have to worry about formatting but just be able to kind of explain like you don''t have to explain.","index":146,"end_time":762.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":755.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And this goes here and that module goes there.","index":147,"end_time":765.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":762.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But here''s that scenario kind of thing.","index":148,"end_time":768.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":765.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And here''s that scenario and what is it meant to do?","index":149,"end_time":770.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":768.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Why do we have it?","index":150,"end_time":771.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":770.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Why is it that we have three separate syncs happening here versus one kind of Thing because what they''re going to do is they''re looking to build something that''s going to be like an alternative to Data Track.","index":151,"end_time":786.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":772.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And I don''t know if they''re going to still, like, build it in a way that is gonna still rely on like a gym like ours to still use a CRM.","index":152,"end_time":795.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":786.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Or they say, hey, we''ll build our own CRM, you know, because it''s ABC Data Track.","index":153,"end_time":800.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":795.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They have their own CRM.","index":154,"end_time":801.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":800.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s just not sophisticated enough, I think, to handle what we.","index":155,"end_time":805.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":801.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What HubSpot does.","index":156,"end_time":806.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":805.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I don''t know that, but that''s kind of for them to kind of think about.","index":157,"end_time":809.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":806.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And it could be like, as we show them this, they realize, oh, like we need to order.","index":158,"end_time":814.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":809.37,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"To build this for the gym properly.","index":159,"end_time":816.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":814.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We need to have.","index":160,"end_time":817.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":816.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We need to kind of release an API, because if they don''t have it work with a CRM, we can''t use it.","index":161,"end_time":824.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":817.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No matter how good the system is, it can''t be used because we can''t build a sales operation on top of it.","index":162,"end_time":829.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":824.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But then if they see them make stuff, they''ll be like, okay, that''s how.","index":163,"end_time":832.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":830.069,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s what we may need to do.","index":164,"end_time":834.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":832.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, yeah, how it''s all communicating.","index":165,"end_time":836.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":834.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":166,"end_time":837.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":836.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, we may.","index":167,"end_time":837.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":837.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The other gems may need to use it this way.","index":168,"end_time":839.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":837.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And I think the critical.","index":169,"end_time":842.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":841.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The HubSpot market, I just, I. I don''t know a lot here.","index":170,"end_time":847.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":843.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I just wrote what I do know.","index":171,"end_time":848.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":847.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So, Milan, you may have to check this work and correct places that I''ve misspoke.","index":172,"end_time":853.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":848.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And let''s put the in scoping stuff.","index":173,"end_time":857.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":855.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Anything that''s in scoping, let''s also write that.","index":174,"end_time":859.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":857.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think it''s.","index":175,"end_time":860.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":859.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s like, I know that E Signature thing is going to be.","index":176,"end_time":864.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":860.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Be an.","index":177,"end_time":864.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":864.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, they should know that because if Data Track offered it, we wouldn''t be doing this whole thing with PandaDoc.","index":178,"end_time":872.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":866.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":179,"end_time":873.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":873.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So anything that''s in scoping, like, just think about what that could be.","index":180,"end_time":878.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":873.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yes.","index":181,"end_time":881.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":880.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I guess one thing I''m missing and realize as I''m doing this is Data Track itself.","index":182,"end_time":885.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":881.27,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But there''s a lot that we.","index":183,"end_time":888.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":886.99,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So maybe, Milan, you may need to add a section of this Data track itself and then just make it general.","index":184,"end_time":896.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":889.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, think about, like the five biggest features of it.","index":185,"end_time":900.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":896.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":186,"end_time":900.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":900.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, the five biggest things that.","index":187,"end_time":902.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":900.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The six figures.","index":188,"end_time":902.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":902.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And you can see how, like, I wasn''t super granular on some of those things.","index":189,"end_time":906.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":902.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I only picked apart the things.","index":190,"end_time":907.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":906.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I know has become issues with Salesforce that we now have sought to resolve through HubSpot.","index":191,"end_time":913.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":907.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But I think maybe you just have one on Data Track as well.","index":192,"end_time":916.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":913.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Got it.","index":193,"end_time":920.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":919.65,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll get that done.","index":194,"end_time":920.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":920.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Which is mostly like, I mean it''s mostly all sales.","index":195,"end_time":924.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":921.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s processing sales and checking people in.","index":196,"end_time":929.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":924.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right when someone comes in, swipe the thing, their face pops up on our screen.","index":197,"end_time":935.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":929.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then processing, processing sales.","index":198,"end_time":937.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":935.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can leave the whole like reporting aspect alone from Data Track because I know that''s a little bit of a new thing.","index":199,"end_time":943.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":937.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Data Track is like moving towards assist a new system that there''s reports that is in Data Track but we don''t have to like, we don''t have to list out all those reports.","index":200,"end_time":953.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":943.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan.","index":201,"end_time":954.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":953.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because I think Max will just want to know like anywhere that where there''s a database you can generate a report.","index":202,"end_time":961.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":954.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So is the report.","index":203,"end_time":962.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":962.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"He just, he, he may want to just know where we go for reports.","index":204,"end_time":967.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":963.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And we''ll just have to say we go to HubSpot to look for reports that is about this kind of stuff.","index":205,"end_time":972.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":967.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And we go to Data Track to pull reports as about that kind of stuff.","index":206,"end_time":976.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":972.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then Max will probably ask some questions about whether or not that makes sense or if they built a system like well, do we need to go like what would we use the reports inside the POS 4 versus inside HubSpot?","index":207,"end_time":991.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":976.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And I don''t.","index":208,"end_time":1000.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":999.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t know how the air call stuff works.","index":209,"end_time":1002.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1000.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So just write that in.","index":210,"end_time":1003.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1002.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that enough, Colin?","index":211,"end_time":1006.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1005.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"For what?","index":212,"end_time":1007.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1007.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know.","index":213,"end_time":1008.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1007.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, what you think?","index":214,"end_time":1010.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1009.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t want.","index":215,"end_time":1012.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1012.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You guys spent like hours and hours on this.","index":216,"end_time":1014.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1012.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This is like.","index":217,"end_time":1015.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1014.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, like I said, I imagine they''ll probably want to see more of like a high level overview of how all these pieces come together and then we can.","index":218,"end_time":1021.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1015.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Any technical information, we can provide that at a later time.","index":219,"end_time":1023.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1021.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, we can do some screenshots and show like how make operations are set up and things like that and.","index":220,"end_time":1029.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1025.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just allude to what''s included and the cost.","index":221,"end_time":1033.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1029.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":222,"end_time":1034.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1033.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What you think?","index":223,"end_time":1034.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1034.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":224,"end_time":1034.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1034.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":225,"end_time":1037.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1037.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so what else is there besides this?","index":226,"end_time":1041.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1038.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So the other thing I was just chatting, we were just chatting with him a lot about was.","index":227,"end_time":1044.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''re doing the facelift project on the Squarespace version of the site.","index":228,"end_time":1047.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1044.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":229,"end_time":1048.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1048.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we''re making progress there and I know we also talked about like getting you know, while we''re doing that facelift, having another project kind of in the works of like a complete upgrade to the website.","index":230,"end_time":1059.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1048.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Moving into like a WordPress environment with a nice builder that''s easy to use if you guys ever want to just make any text changes on your own.","index":231,"end_time":1066.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1060.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But so we have 25 hours in this Month left, and they''re largely dedicated obviously to HubSpot and the facelift project.","index":232,"end_time":1074.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1067.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so I wanted to chat through if you wanted to like, maybe set up a.","index":233,"end_time":1078.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1075.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just a project fee for a website build instead of using our hours each month, because that will limit the speed and pace that we can build a website.","index":234,"end_time":1087.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1078.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One is, do we have other hours?","index":235,"end_time":1094.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1092.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Have we already used up the hours from the past?","index":236,"end_time":1096.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1094.02,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, you know how we.","index":237,"end_time":1097.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1096.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"For a period?","index":238,"end_time":1098.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1097.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, so all hours rollover.","index":239,"end_time":1099.859,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1098.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We don''t do any of the, like, half from the last month rollover anymore.","index":240,"end_time":1103.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1099.859,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like any hours you purchase, you get access to.","index":241,"end_time":1105.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1103.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so have we all caught up?","index":242,"end_time":1108.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1106.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Are you saying, like, we''ve caught up now to.","index":243,"end_time":1110.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1108.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"To.","index":244,"end_time":1110.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1110.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we just have 25 hours this month?","index":245,"end_time":1113.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1110.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, so we have 24 left.","index":246,"end_time":1114.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1113.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was just refreshed at the beginning of the month with the 29 hours that you guys purchase every month.","index":247,"end_time":1119.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1114.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":248,"end_time":1130.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1130.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Were there.","index":249,"end_time":1132.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1131.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Would you.","index":250,"end_time":1132.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1132.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Were there any hours that.","index":251,"end_time":1134.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1133.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t remember?","index":252,"end_time":1138.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1137.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, we.","index":253,"end_time":1138.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1138.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"For.","index":254,"end_time":1138.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1138.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I. I think like for a period of a few months, we had hours that we didn''t really.","index":255,"end_time":1144.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1138.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We didn''t use at all.","index":256,"end_time":1145.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1144.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Was there.","index":257,"end_time":1146.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1146.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Was that all rolled over, like, from way back when?","index":258,"end_time":1149.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1146.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, so we had 188 hours purchased.","index":259,"end_time":1152.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1150.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ve credited 22 and a quarter hours.","index":260,"end_time":1155.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1153.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it should include everything because I know we''ve done a lot of HubSpot work in.","index":261,"end_time":1160.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1156.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"In the past two months, especially that have gone back towards these hours.","index":262,"end_time":1165.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1160.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ve delivered 180 so far.","index":263,"end_time":1169.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1167.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":264,"end_time":1171.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1170.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How many hours do we need to save for HubSpot this month?","index":265,"end_time":1175.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1171.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I would say we usually need a bucket of 10.","index":266,"end_time":1180.056,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1176.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"10Amonth.","index":267,"end_time":1181.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1180.264,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it.","index":268,"end_time":1183.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1181.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It will probably go down, you know, as we keep going.","index":269,"end_time":1186.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1183.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":270,"end_time":1187.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1187.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What else is what, Milan?","index":271,"end_time":1190.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1187.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, it still seems like every day there''s something going on.","index":272,"end_time":1192.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1190.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like when.","index":273,"end_time":1193.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1192.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"When can we reach a place of like, some core things?","index":274,"end_time":1200.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1193.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Can.","index":275,"end_time":1200.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1200.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is working fine.","index":276,"end_time":1201.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1200.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I know there''s like, tweaks and things, but, like, is it like every day we''re coming up with something, oh, we want it to happen like this.","index":277,"end_time":1208.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1201.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This should be happening like that.","index":278,"end_time":1209.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1208.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Or is the work slowing down already?","index":279,"end_time":1212.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1209.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think the work is slowing down with.","index":280,"end_time":1214.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1212.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"With like the system or process or workflow changes.","index":281,"end_time":1218.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1214.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There are.","index":282,"end_time":1219.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1218.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, HubSpot does break.","index":283,"end_time":1221.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1219.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, for example, the last two days we.","index":284,"end_time":1224.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1222.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We had to put in some work there because the core stuff that my reps needed weren''t working.","index":285,"end_time":1230.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1225.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So why was that the case?","index":286,"end_time":1233,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1231.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Nina just gave the technical answer.","index":287,"end_time":1239.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1234.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you want to.","index":288,"end_time":1239.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1239.28,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Want to go ahead and give?","index":289,"end_time":1241,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1240.04,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we added the separate workflow flow to the list that we already have.","index":290,"end_time":1246.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1241.64,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So we have one list that''s the hot list and the other list is the club visited list.","index":291,"end_time":1253.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1246.93,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And we wanted to have a separate list so we can see which which contacts from our contact lists have have reinquired or reinquired.","index":292,"end_time":1267.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1253.01,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So we can have contacts that are hotter than the hot list.","index":293,"end_time":1272.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1267.49,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So for example, for them to show up sooner than those that are might not be as interested.","index":294,"end_time":1277.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1272.17,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Is that because how much of like.","index":295,"end_time":1281.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1277.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that the way that we designed it to begin with or was that a.","index":296,"end_time":1284.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1281.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Was that other bugs in.","index":297,"end_time":1286.689,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1285.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Was that like an error like we told.","index":298,"end_time":1289.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1287.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We intended for that to happen and that wasn''t done correctly earlier or it.","index":299,"end_time":1296.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1289.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Wasn''T imagined from the start to have for example, last activity.","index":300,"end_time":1300.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1296.05,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":301,"end_time":1301.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1301.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we had discussed that with Aaron at the beginning when we imagined HubSpot we knew that there weren''t going to be any like duplicate leads.","index":302,"end_time":1315,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1302.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we knew that when leads would re inquire right.","index":303,"end_time":1317.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1315,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The actual like prospect account would have to have some kind of property which said that they re inquired.","index":304,"end_time":1323.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1317.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"With everything going on, it kind of like fell off I guess and now we kind of like restarted it.","index":305,"end_time":1332.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1324.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then the last two days there was something going on with the workflows all working at the same time.","index":306,"end_time":1337.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1333.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then when you add an additional workflow, sometimes HubSpot doesn''t.","index":307,"end_time":1342.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1337.19,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Doesn''t automatically catch that contact is in two different workflows.","index":308,"end_time":1349.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1344.35,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And then it''s that it''s fine that they''re there so it manually removes them.","index":309,"end_time":1355.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1349.87,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So now we separate times for each workflow so that doesn''t happen.","index":310,"end_time":1359.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1355.07,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And now all contexts are going into both lists.","index":311,"end_time":1361.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1359.13,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"How much of the make work is.","index":312,"end_time":1363.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1362.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is.","index":313,"end_time":1364.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1364.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is still left to do?","index":314,"end_time":1366.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1364.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Have we kind of no longer updating things on that front?","index":315,"end_time":1370.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1366.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t think we''ve had a touch make in the past week.","index":316,"end_time":1374.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1371.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Did you guys.","index":317,"end_time":1375.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1374.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I, when I logged in to just looked at it, it looked like you guys like relabel some things and, and just kind of.","index":318,"end_time":1380.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1375.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Did you guys end up kind of like reconfiguring a whole lot of it when I look at.","index":319,"end_time":1384.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1380.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I''m not.","index":320,"end_time":1385.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1384.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think.","index":321,"end_time":1386.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1385.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think that part, if that part''s stable, everything else is HubSpot configuration.","index":322,"end_time":1391.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1386.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We really need this month to sort of I think finish the HubSpot work.","index":323,"end_time":1395.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1391.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can''t be, I think six, four months, five months in and, and solving this level of thing.","index":324,"end_time":1403.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1395.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":325,"end_time":1404.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1403.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What Milan is saying about this is something that we raised initially.","index":326,"end_time":1407.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1404.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Not pointing fingers doesn''t really matter.","index":327,"end_time":1410.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1408.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s just that''s a Core thing.","index":328,"end_time":1412.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1410.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s a core thing.","index":329,"end_time":1413.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1412.54,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So Milan, that''s also on us at the gym to.","index":330,"end_time":1417.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1413.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"To.","index":331,"end_time":1417.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1417.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If we see we.","index":332,"end_time":1419.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1418.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean we tell you that right away but we need to make sure like that we''re.","index":333,"end_time":1424.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1419.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Any problems we''re experiencing that and telling you that as soon as possible so we can work on that this month.","index":334,"end_time":1431.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1424.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I can''t imagine like going into December we''d be solving these type of problems, but rather like it''s just kind of new functions.","index":335,"end_time":1439.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1432.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":336,"end_time":1439.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1439.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"New things we want to see happen.","index":337,"end_time":1441.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1439.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This is something that I would put in the bucket of.","index":338,"end_time":1444.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1441.97,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It is core.","index":339,"end_time":1446.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1445.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know, it just.","index":340,"end_time":1447.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1447.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s many things to do, but it is a core thing.","index":341,"end_time":1450.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1448.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What about the like, Milan, like, is there anything else that is when you think of like when we use Salesforce, like things that you think is still core in the sense that it''s not a new thing that we didn''t do before with Salesforce.","index":342,"end_time":1470.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1450.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think the biggest change that we made was last week with the lead sources and the contact methods that we finally got that working correctly.","index":343,"end_time":1481.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1471.29,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Other than that, I think most of the major priorities or the main functions.","index":344,"end_time":1488.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1483.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We''ve got it all sorted out on HubSpot at this point.","index":345,"end_time":1491.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1489.21,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Are the drip campaigns on the automated emails to the past?","index":346,"end_time":1495.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1491.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The past two drip campaigns are on the.","index":347,"end_time":1498.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1495.69,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What about new lead drift campaigns are on meta.","index":348,"end_time":1503.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1498.21,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Meta leads as well.","index":349,"end_time":1504.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1503.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I need to.","index":350,"end_time":1507.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1506.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean I would assume so I need to double check.","index":351,"end_time":1510.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1508.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Is that right?","index":352,"end_time":1512.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1511.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Colin, do you know if every.","index":353,"end_time":1514.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1512.37,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It should be any.","index":354,"end_time":1516.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1515.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That lead.","index":355,"end_time":1517.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1516.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Any of those lead sources.","index":356,"end_time":1518.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1517.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sorry, go ahead, keep going.","index":357,"end_time":1529.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1528.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Milan.","index":358,"end_time":1530.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1529.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m going to pull up the workflow.","index":359,"end_time":1531.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1530.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":360,"end_time":1532.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1532.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So those two drip campaigns are working.","index":361,"end_time":1534.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1532.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think one of the biggest things that we also need to discuss is the SMS marketing drip campaigns that we potentially want to set up IFE on HubSpot but that would be really the final like big change on HubSpot.","index":362,"end_time":1555.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1536.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s kind of it.","index":363,"end_time":1559.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1558.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you.","index":364,"end_time":1563.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1562.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How comfortable do you.","index":365,"end_time":1564.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1563.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you feel, Milan, with like managing the MQLs, the marketing segments under all of that?","index":366,"end_time":1573.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1564.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So general flow, like you''re turning some things on, you''re turning some things off.","index":367,"end_time":1577.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1573.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that correct?","index":368,"end_time":1579.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1577.89,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Correct.","index":369,"end_time":1579.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1579.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":370,"end_time":1580.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1579.65,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I.","index":371,"end_time":1580.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1580.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"At the moment I''ve only turned things on because it''s only been a month, but.","index":372,"end_time":1584.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1580.33,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":373,"end_time":1585.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1585.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And we still have some.","index":374,"end_time":1587.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1586.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Some space there.","index":375,"end_time":1588.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1587.41,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":376,"end_time":1589.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1588.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Confirm that meta is in there.","index":377,"end_time":1590.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1589.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Meta''s okay.","index":378,"end_time":1591.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1590.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So.","index":379,"end_time":1591.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1591.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And the same thing with all the website forms.","index":380,"end_time":1593.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1591.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yep.","index":381,"end_time":1594.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1593.69,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Last week I think Aaron was like saying that or two weeks ago that there was.","index":382,"end_time":1600.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1595.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"She couldn''t confirm if like leads were coming properly into HubSpot do you remember that Milan?","index":383,"end_time":1610.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1604.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like it was like we looked at.","index":384,"end_time":1613.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1610.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It was like to this point the lead the drip campaign.","index":385,"end_time":1617,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1613.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":386,"end_time":1617.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1617.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think we heard like it was only reaching like a number of people.","index":387,"end_time":1622.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1617.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Then we''re like no, we have way more number of people than that.","index":388,"end_time":1625.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1622.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you remember that right conversation?","index":389,"end_time":1627.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1625.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I think it was.","index":390,"end_time":1629.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1627.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"She.","index":391,"end_time":1629.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1629.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"She did like an expected number of of marketing leads per.","index":392,"end_time":1636.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1629.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Per like group.","index":393,"end_time":1637.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1637,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The new lead trip campaign had something like 150 incoming leads total which was just off.","index":394,"end_time":1649.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1639.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we need to the email drip campaigns.","index":395,"end_time":1654.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1650.04,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean I''m just gonna have a look right now and see how many.","index":396,"end_time":1657.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1654.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s weird right?","index":397,"end_time":1658.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1658.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Colin, do you know like we heard not that long ago, like two weeks ago that there were a very small number of those emails being sent and she was like in HubSpot looks like this number has been sent.","index":398,"end_time":1672.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1659.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But we know we have more than that on meta leads alone.","index":399,"end_time":1676.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1672.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So yeah, I remember the meta leads conversation and that was those were matching up because the only discrepancy in like the 289 versus the 311 or something.","index":400,"end_time":1688.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1677.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think Milan that you had sent over in that spreadsheet was it was 289 new people and the other ones had reconverted.","index":401,"end_time":1695.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1688.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So all of those contacts re inquired or what you mean like filled out the form again on Facebook.","index":402,"end_time":1701.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1696.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so we would still send those people the same emails right like each time they fill out a form or we would not send those people the drip campaign.","index":403,"end_time":1713.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1702.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If they reinforced I would, I would.","index":404,"end_time":1715.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1713.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Put them back into the drip campaign.","index":405,"end_time":1717.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1715.28,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, they, I mean they reinquired.","index":406,"end_time":1719.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1717.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, her.","index":407,"end_time":1723.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1722.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Her numbers were completely off.","index":408,"end_time":1724.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1723.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t think she looked at the, the drip campaign because the number one lead drip campaign email has 1022 leads that it''s been delivered to.","index":409,"end_time":1737.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1724.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Since when?","index":410,"end_time":1738.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1737.56,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well it got turned on again like last month so in the last two months basically it says that it was last.","index":411,"end_time":1745.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1739,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Can we do that Holland to.","index":412,"end_time":1747.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1745.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"To push that the lead drip campaigns to anybody who also whether they''re new or re inquired they should get those emails.","index":413,"end_time":1757.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1747.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we can turn re enroll back on for those.","index":414,"end_time":1761.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1759.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then so, so looking ahead there''s text messages and the docus the panda doc thing we need to do.","index":415,"end_time":1775.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1766.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think.","index":416,"end_time":1779.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1778.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well from testing it I, I don''t think the reps liked it.","index":417,"end_time":1785.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1779.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I didn''t end up loving the the system either.","index":418,"end_time":1788.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1785.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And I think we''re just going to stick to people having to come in in person and sign their agreement and it''ll just be stuck in the queue until they do.","index":419,"end_time":1796.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1788.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And what was wrong?","index":420,"end_time":1798.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1797.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What didn''t make sense with the system moving forward?","index":421,"end_time":1802.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1799.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Why didn''t it make sense?","index":422,"end_time":1804.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1803.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, why didn''t they like it?","index":423,"end_time":1806.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1804.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s just having to manually input all the information.","index":424,"end_time":1810.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1807.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"For a large number of like people who sign up on.","index":425,"end_time":1815.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1811.12,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Over the phone was time consuming.","index":426,"end_time":1820.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1815.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then for the, I think it was, I think they sent out like three or four.","index":427,"end_time":1825.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1820.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"None of them signed.","index":428,"end_time":1827.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1826.28,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So they don''t have to do that on the live call.","index":429,"end_time":1834.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1830.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They can send it after the call, right?","index":430,"end_time":1837.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1834.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They can send it, yeah.","index":431,"end_time":1839.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1837.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It would only be done after the call.","index":432,"end_time":1841.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1839.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So they, they don''t like to do the work.","index":433,"end_time":1843.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1841.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And we don''t have people signing this as expected because people paid it.","index":434,"end_time":1847.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1843.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, I don''t want to do this, not important.","index":435,"end_time":1849.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1847.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''ll just do it when I show up.","index":436,"end_time":1850.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1849.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then what about.","index":437,"end_time":1852.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1851.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay, okay.","index":438,"end_time":1857.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1853.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So with this SMS work, how many hours is that going to take to get this set up?","index":439,"end_time":1864.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1858.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This sounds like it''s just HubSpot turning something on and then.","index":440,"end_time":1867.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1864.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m not sure off the top of my head.","index":441,"end_time":1870.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1867.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''d have to dive into, see how many hours it would take.","index":442,"end_time":1873.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1870.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And did you know?","index":443,"end_time":1874.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1873.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Go ahead.","index":444,"end_time":1875.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1875.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You''re talking about setting up SMS marketing.","index":445,"end_time":1878.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1876.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":446,"end_time":1880.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1880,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And, and what is the Air calls like approach to this?","index":447,"end_time":1883.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1880.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Air Coal is a, they use like a third party company which is called Marker, I forget what the name is.","index":448,"end_time":1892.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1884.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Right.","index":449,"end_time":1893.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1892.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But basically the entire, it looks like ring DNA.","index":450,"end_time":1897.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1893.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Their entire like SMS platform for the reps would be on a separate software and then they would be able to do, the reps would be able to do their individual bulk texts and respond to those texts as they come in.","index":451,"end_time":1912.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1897.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Whereas HubSpot would just have like the one marketing SMS number that they would send out.","index":452,"end_time":1917.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1912.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"SMS marketing, what''s the cost difference between both options?","index":453,"end_time":1925.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1920.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it''s like almost 500 bucks.","index":454,"end_time":1928.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1925.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"500 or 600 bucks?","index":455,"end_time":1930.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1928.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Almost is the difference.","index":456,"end_time":1931.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1930.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So HubSpot''s the cheaper version, but obviously the Air call system has a lot more to offer than HubSpot does.","index":457,"end_time":1941.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1931.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And what would we use these messages for?","index":458,"end_time":1944.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1942.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we would do like whenever there would be like an offer drop or whenever somebody would first inquire or if they missed their appointment.","index":459,"end_time":1955.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1946.12,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Any kind of like workflow that we wanted to create, we would be able to set up like an automated SMS system and then the SMS responses would just automatically either be put in a list if we''re using HubSpot or would be direct responses to the reps and the reps will just be able to communicate with them.","index":460,"end_time":1977.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1955.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How would we.","index":461,"end_time":1979.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1978.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So can you give me an Example of I get this text and I say I''m interested.","index":462,"end_time":1985.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1979.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Does that show them on your lead list that you got a notification that.","index":463,"end_time":1990.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1986.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I respond on HubSpot?","index":464,"end_time":1993.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1990.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t know like anywhere.","index":465,"end_time":1995.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1994.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like how would you know that I respond?","index":466,"end_time":1996.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1995.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it''s dependent.","index":467,"end_time":1998.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1997.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So on HubSpot it would drop into a lead list and then the contact owner, I mean we would set this up Colin, where the contact owner would get an email notification saying that one of their leads just responded to the SMS text and then they would go in and they would reach out to them off of their personal like air called phone numbers.","index":468,"end_time":2018.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1998.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If we were using the Air Call SMS system then it would just respond into their SMS software which would be their like texting platform or whatever and they would just be doing two way conversations.","index":469,"end_time":2032.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2019.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You remind me, don''t we already do some text messaging on Air Call?","index":470,"end_time":2035.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2032.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So is it a different platform than what''s already there?","index":471,"end_time":2038.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2036,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It would be a different platform, yeah.","index":472,"end_time":2040.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2038.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So what, what would happen is we would stop doing text messaging on Air Call.","index":473,"end_time":2044.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2040.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We would only do calls and then we would have to use this third system to be able to just text message and it''s like a, it''s like already connected to Air Call I think.","index":474,"end_time":2056.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2044.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean it sounds like one way to do it is like you can start with the cheaper option because it''s cheaper and if people, if that seems like to be a great viable way to grow leads that way and get engagement, we can then determine what is causing those people to respond.","index":475,"end_time":2075.499,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2056.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is it the automated triggers from HubSpot?","index":476,"end_time":2079.179,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2075.819,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because I don''t know if aircall can do that.","index":477,"end_time":2081.459,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2079.179,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you know if aircall can, we can set up triggers based on HubSpot status or what they, what form they entered.","index":478,"end_time":2090.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2081.459,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I believe they can.","index":479,"end_time":2096.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2094.23,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''m not, I don''t want to misspeak though.","index":480,"end_time":2099.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2098.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But yes, I believe they can.","index":481,"end_time":2100.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2099.67,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Can you, can you find out like how that works?","index":482,"end_time":2104.789,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2101.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know like the question would be like someone fills out a meta lead, how, how does it happen that they get a text message from Aircall?","index":483,"end_time":2112.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2104.789,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Aircall?","index":484,"end_time":2113.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2112.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is it through the integration with HubSpot?","index":485,"end_time":2115.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2113.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is it configured inside HubSpot or is it configured inside Aircall?","index":486,"end_time":2118.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2115.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because I, I know the HubSpot UI is you can set up those automations but now we''re creating this other.","index":487,"end_time":2126.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2120.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Not Air Call but it''s another third party text messaging system.","index":488,"end_time":2130.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2127.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So does that, what, what does that look like to, you know what I mean?","index":489,"end_time":2133.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2130.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"To connect.","index":490,"end_time":2134.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2133.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yes.","index":491,"end_time":2135.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2135.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The triggers to that thing.","index":492,"end_time":2137.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2135.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So why don''t you email them but you know, like, while you find that out, I''m.","index":493,"end_time":2141.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2137.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m leaning towards the HubSpot work because we know how it works, we know how to set the automations of those SMSs.","index":494,"end_time":2147.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2141.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we''ll be able to do this fairly.","index":495,"end_time":2149.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2147.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We should be able to do this fairly quickly and troubleshoot if something goes wrong in this like period of launch.","index":496,"end_time":2156.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2149.56,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So 20 hours.","index":497,"end_time":2158.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2156.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"20.","index":498,"end_time":2159.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2158.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t know, like the website isn''t.","index":499,"end_time":2162.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2159.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know, like I would say like five, five hours.","index":500,"end_time":2166.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2163.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Making small things in Squarespace.","index":501,"end_time":2168.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2166.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean is that fair Colin, given what you''re hearing, like spend the time to between more edits on HubSpot plus this SMS thing this month.","index":502,"end_time":2180.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2169.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":503,"end_time":2182.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2181.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So like, I mean the Squarespace and HubSpot stuff is totally fine within the hours that we have for this month.","index":504,"end_time":2187.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2182.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was talking more about like we talked about a larger website, like full build, redesign.","index":505,"end_time":2192.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2187.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s what I was talking about for a different like contract.","index":506,"end_time":2194.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2192.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, no, let''s keep this here for now because I think just keep making whatever you think is needed for Squarespace, those small UI stuff.","index":507,"end_time":2205.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2195.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Responsiveness, you know, and you''ll run out and it''s.","index":508,"end_time":2210.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2206.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think we will some point need to move towards a different system.","index":509,"end_time":2217.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2210.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And I just thought Alex, about this last night, like we need to do some invest.","index":510,"end_time":2226.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2218.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We need to, you know, for something like that we need to compare the costs not just with you guys, but we need to look.","index":511,"end_time":2231.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2226.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Look and because it''s a bigger effort and we may want to do like an online store.","index":512,"end_time":2237.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2231.61,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":513,"end_time":2238.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2238.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"With stuff.","index":514,"end_time":2239.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2238.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we need to integrate with some kind of online point of sale.","index":515,"end_time":2245.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2239.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it''s, it just takes a little bit more planning on what we need and how.","index":516,"end_time":2251.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2247.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re not sure if what that cost would be and how long it would take to complete.","index":517,"end_time":2257.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2252.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":518,"end_time":2259.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2258.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So but for now just do the Squarespace.","index":519,"end_time":2262.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2259.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":520,"end_time":2263.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2262.7,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And even as part of the Squarespace we had mentioned Shopify and like having even just like a button to go to the store.","index":521,"end_time":2267.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2263.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that''s pretty easy for us to do.","index":522,"end_time":2270.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2268.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If we wanted to do like a more integrated, you know, if we do build a website we could have like Shopify as its own page on the actual website itself.","index":523,"end_time":2277.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2270.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":524,"end_time":2281.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2281.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Why, why don''t we.","index":525,"end_time":2283.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2281.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":526,"end_time":2283.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2283.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Let''s just focus on what we have now between all of this and.","index":527,"end_time":2288.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2283.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean Milan, you just try to keep breaking it.","index":528,"end_time":2294.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2290.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Of course this has to.","index":529,"end_time":2297.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2295.7,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We, we.","index":530,"end_time":2297.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2297.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I feel like we have to put.","index":531,"end_time":2299.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2297.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Draw some like as a team like draw some line on like when this has reached a point of stability here.","index":532,"end_time":2304.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2299.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, Milan said he logged in today and he hasn''t found anything.","index":533,"end_time":2308.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2305.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":534,"end_time":2309.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2308.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I don''t.","index":535,"end_time":2309.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2309.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that it''s got to be like one week.","index":536,"end_time":2311.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2309.61,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"One week that you can go Milan without bothering Colin and Nina about anything.","index":537,"end_time":2316.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2311.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":538,"end_time":2318.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2318.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like right now I don''t think you can confidently say that if they walked away.","index":539,"end_time":2322.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2319.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You can''t confidently say something''s not going to break.","index":540,"end_time":2326.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2323.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But like you guys are confident, you guys and us to work together and build something, it needs to go a week, you know, without one of us going, I don''t understand.","index":541,"end_time":2337.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2326.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Or this lead isn''t dropping in correctly.","index":542,"end_time":2340.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2337.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"When that day happens, Colin, Nina are gonna miss me.","index":543,"end_time":2344.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2341.96,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, so on the sms, I think it''s on.","index":544,"end_time":2352.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2348.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Why don''t we.","index":545,"end_time":2353.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2352.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan.","index":546,"end_time":2353.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2353.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We.","index":547,"end_time":2353.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2353.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Let''s.","index":548,"end_time":2354.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2353.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I have a. I have a call with the HubSpot rep at 4pm today.","index":549,"end_time":2360.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2356.04,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":550,"end_time":2361.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2361.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Find out some more details about it.","index":551,"end_time":2363.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2361.56,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I.","index":552,"end_time":2363.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2363.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s.","index":553,"end_time":2364.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2363.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What f. How much is it going to be additional?","index":554,"end_time":2366.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2364.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It is like $500, $600 additional.","index":555,"end_time":2371.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2368.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If we wanted to go the hay market route, which is the air call.","index":556,"end_time":2374.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2371.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What about company?","index":557,"end_time":2375.919,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2374.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How much is it for HubSpot?","index":558,"end_time":2377.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2376.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s around 600.","index":559,"end_time":2380.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2378.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"600.","index":560,"end_time":2381.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2380.56,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it''s 1100 for air call.","index":561,"end_time":2383.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2381.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":562,"end_time":2384.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2383.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Um, yeah, because they have a per SMS charge, which is more expensive than hunt spawning.","index":563,"end_time":2393.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2385.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think HubSpot''s like much cheaper.","index":564,"end_time":2395.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2393.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, find out more details and then let''s.","index":565,"end_time":2400.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2396.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If we agree to do it, let''s do it and then we''ll have.","index":566,"end_time":2403.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2400.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s probably some setup that colony you can help us put together.","index":567,"end_time":2408.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2404.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we can build flows and everything.","index":568,"end_time":2409.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2408.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you.","index":569,"end_time":2412.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2411.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, teach.","index":570,"end_time":2413.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2412.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then you can teach Milan how to edit the content.","index":571,"end_time":2416,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2413.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And is creating flow something that Milan can learn?","index":572,"end_time":2419.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2416.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like if we wanted to run a flow mid month on something, is it like, is it hard to do?","index":573,"end_time":2425.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2419.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No, it''s more just knowing all of like the properties that you want to tap into, which Milan is definitely getting familiar with.","index":574,"end_time":2432.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2426.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean when you set up workflow, you basically just say like, this is what triggers this to start or someone to enroll.","index":575,"end_time":2438.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2432.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Uh, and then you walk through like the logic of.","index":576,"end_time":2440.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2438.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have you seen the flows that have been built already?","index":577,"end_time":2442.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2440.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Have you seen the flows page and how HubSpot logic works?","index":578,"end_time":2445.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2442.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I have, yeah.","index":579,"end_time":2447.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2446.41,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ve, I''ve gone digging in there.","index":580,"end_time":2449.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2447.53,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I haven''t changed anything.","index":581,"end_time":2450.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2449.29,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You haven''t changed.","index":582,"end_time":2451.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2450.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Um, okay, so I think, I think that''s fine.","index":583,"end_time":2457.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2452.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like maybe it''s a decision we can make when we''re in town, Milan with Alex and we look at this together.","index":584,"end_time":2466.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2457.61,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It.","index":585,"end_time":2466.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2466.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is there any way they can give Us, I mean, find out if they could give us a trial or something.","index":586,"end_time":2471.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2466.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can try.","index":587,"end_time":2471.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2471.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":588,"end_time":2473.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2472.98,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"For like a month.","index":589,"end_time":2475.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2473.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Maybe not.","index":590,"end_time":2478.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2478.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay, do that because it''s sms.","index":591,"end_time":2480.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2478.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But.","index":592,"end_time":2481.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2480.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The other thing, Milan, to keep in mind there is if you do go HubSpot, does any of like the routing or porting need to happen again for the phone numbers?","index":593,"end_time":2496.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2485.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Think that''s going to happen again?","index":594,"end_time":2501.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2500.43,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think it''s just going to be off of one phone number.","index":595,"end_time":2504.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2502.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, there will be limits.","index":596,"end_time":2508.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2507.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right now that you know this, you should find out like what the limits are.","index":597,"end_time":2511.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2508.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If it is a single number, if we''re incorrect, everything like one Club one has one, Club two has one.","index":598,"end_time":2519.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2511.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And.","index":599,"end_time":2521.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2520.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And they should know we also use Air Call.","index":600,"end_time":2522.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2521.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Does this interfere with things.","index":601,"end_time":2526.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2522.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m writing these questions down.","index":602,"end_time":2534.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2533,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll get answers.","index":603,"end_time":2535.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2534.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What?","index":604,"end_time":2537,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2536.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean, do you need this team to be part of this call?","index":605,"end_time":2542,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2538.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan?","index":606,"end_time":2542.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2542,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like, I mean, if you guys.","index":607,"end_time":2549.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2543.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":608,"end_time":2551.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2549.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t.","index":609,"end_time":2552.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2551.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think it only be helpful.","index":610,"end_time":2554.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2552.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you have that already scheduled?","index":611,"end_time":2557.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2556.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Milan.","index":612,"end_time":2557.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2557.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Do give me two seconds here because I rescheduled it.","index":613,"end_time":2565.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2560.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s at 2pm today.","index":614,"end_time":2568.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2566.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I can''t make that.","index":615,"end_time":2571.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2569.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When can you available Tomorrow?","index":616,"end_time":2576.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2573.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I do have 2pm tomorrow.","index":617,"end_time":2579.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2577.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Does 2pm tomorrow work, Milan?","index":618,"end_time":2589.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2587.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m gonna email him right now and I''ll let you know.","index":619,"end_time":2593.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2591.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, just let''s include.","index":620,"end_time":2594.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2593.37,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think it ends up just being faster.","index":621,"end_time":2599.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2596.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If you guys are building this for us, you can ask the questions as well.","index":622,"end_time":2603.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2599.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then we''ll have to schedule more meetings with HubSpot to know how it works.","index":623,"end_time":2609.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2603.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Pollen, if you have like a list of questions already that you, you can think of top of mind, just send them over to me too and then I can just ask him if you can''t make the meeting.","index":624,"end_time":2619.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2610.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":625,"end_time":2620.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2619.87,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right.","index":626,"end_time":2622.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2622.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, so we''ll.","index":627,"end_time":2623.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2622.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For the critical workflows document, we''ll have that all ready to send out tomorrow for you guys to send that over to Motion iq.","index":628,"end_time":2631.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2623.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then Milan, if anything happens on HubSpot, let us know and we''ll check into it and then we''ll keep working on the facelift to Squarespace.","index":629,"end_time":2640.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2631.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Got it?","index":630,"end_time":2643.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2642.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":631,"end_time":2644.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2644.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, thank you all.","index":632,"end_time":2646.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2644.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":633,"end_time":2647.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2647.16,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":634,"end_time":2648.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2647.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you guys.","index":635,"end_time":2649.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2648.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"}],"dateString":"2025-11-05T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86061042503?pwd=x0TBEgRs7qFmrRIEItauCzbH71kaq8.1","participants":["yefei@yhatinvest.com,alex.white@yhatinvest.com,tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com,wyattc@yhatinvest.com,robert.rudder@powerhousesoflo.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,tatiana.fernandez@powerhousesoflo.com,milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com,nina.belina@marketersindemand.com,cristina@pgmia.com,milan@pgmia.com","yefei@yhatinvest.com","alex.white@yhatinvest.com","tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com","wyattc@yhatinvest.com","robert.rudder@powerhousesoflo.com","tatiana.fernandez@powerhousesoflo.com","milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com","nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","cristina@pgmia.com","milan@pgmia.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01K8RB8XGTN1JP7J2CV9DWB169","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.88,"bullets":["Resolved parallel workflow conflicts in HubSpot that caused lead list inconsistencies.","Confirmed HubSpot performance stabilizing; core workflows now operating as intended.","Discussed using HubSpot SMS over Aircall’s solution due to lower costs and simpler setup.","Agreed website facelift and HubSpot fixes will proceed within current 25-hour monthly budget.","Planned to deliver screenshots and updated integration documentation to partners by Thursday."],"highlights":[{"quote":"So now we fixed it so it doesn''t overlap.","speaker":"Nina Belina"},{"quote":"Other than that, I think most of the major priorities... we''ve got it all sorted out.","speaker":"Milan Wagner"},{"quote":"We really need this month to sort of... finish the HubSpot work.","speaker":"Yefei Jin"}],"topics":["delivery","hubspot","workflow","sms","website"],"model":"openai/gpt-4","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-11-13T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **HubSpot System Stabilization and Workflow Optimization**\n\nThe team agreed that the core HubSpot system is nearing stability, with ongoing fixes focused on workflow overlaps and lead management (07:44).\n\n- **Nina Belina reported resolving parallel workflow conflicts in HubSpot** by staggering start times, preventing contacts from being manually removed from lists (07:44)\n    - This fix ensures contacts now appear correctly in both the hot and club visited lists without overlap.\n    - Milan Wagner confirmed that sales added a \"last activity\" or \"last engagement\" date column to track contact interactions more accurately.\n    - Nina clarified that HubSpot can only track context and activity going forward, not retroactively.\n    - This update reduces daily system errors and improves lead tracking accuracy.\n\n- **Milan Wagner and Yefei Jin agreed that HubSpot work remains the priority for this month**, reserving a **bucket of about 10 hours** monthly for ongoing HubSpot support and tweaks (19:30)\n    - Colin Costigan confirmed **24 hours remain for this month’s work**, refreshed with a new purchase of **29 hours** at the start of the month (09:56).\n    - The team expects HubSpot issues to taper off as workflows mature, aiming to avoid core fixes extending into December.\n    - Yefei emphasized the need for early issue reporting to prevent prolonged workflow problems.\n    - Milan noted that recent fixes on lead sources and contact methods have addressed most core HubSpot priorities (24:31).\n\n- **Marketing drip campaigns are active and being validated for effectiveness**, with particular attention to Facebook meta leads and re-enrolling reinquired contacts (25:17)\n    - Milan shared that the lead drip campaign has delivered emails to **1,022 leads** over two months and confirmed re-enrollment for repeat inquires will be turned back on.\n    - Colin clarified that meta lead counts from HubSpot closely match form submissions, with minor differences due to reinquiries.\n    - The team agreed all website form leads funnel through HubSpot workflows.\n    - Ensuring drip campaigns reach all appropriate leads remains a key performance metric.\n\n## **SMS Marketing Integration and Platform Evaluation**\n\nThe group is weighing options between HubSpot’s SMS marketing feature and Aircall’s third-party SMS platform, balancing cost and functionality (31:20).\n\n- **HubSpot SMS marketing was favored for initial rollout due to lower costs and easier automation setup**, with estimated additional costs around **$600** (39:38)\n    - Milan reported Aircall’s SMS platform costs approximately **$1,100 total** including per-message fees, nearly double HubSpot’s price (39:43).\n    - HubSpot supports automated SMS triggered by lead status or form submissions, facilitating marketing workflows.\n    - Milan is tasked with clarifying integration and trigger details between HubSpot, Aircall, and third-party SMS tools.\n    - Yefei emphasized the value of starting with the cheaper HubSpot option for quicker setup and troubleshooting.\n\n- **SMS marketing use cases include automated notifications for offers, first inquiries, and missed appointments**, enhancing engagement (32:26)\n    - Responses to SMS messages would notify contact owners via email for follow-up through Aircall or HubSpot.\n    - HubSpot would consolidate SMS replies into lead lists, while Aircall offers two-way texting within reps’ personal SMS platforms.\n    - Milan has a scheduled call with a HubSpot rep to gather more technical details and pricing clarifications (39:16).\n    - The team plans to test SMS flows and train Milan on editing and running campaigns to enable agile mid-month adjustments.\n\n## **Website Development Strategy and Resource Allocation**\n\nThe team is balancing ongoing small fixes on the current Squarespace site against a potential larger WordPress redesign, mindful of resource constraints (09:39).\n\n- **Colin explained that the current monthly hours (around 25) are mostly allocated between HubSpot and Squarespace facelift work**, limiting capacity for a full WordPress rebuild without additional contracts (10:18)\n    - The option to start a WordPress redesign was discussed but would consume hours rapidly, leaving no time for HubSpot improvements.\n    - Yefei suggested continuing small UI fixes on Squarespace for now, emphasizing planning for a future larger site build with e-commerce and POS integration.\n    - Colin noted Shopify integration could be added as a simple button in Squarespace or as a dedicated page in a new WordPress site.\n    - The team is deferring any major website overhaul until a comprehensive cost and timeline comparison is completed.\n\n- **The team confirmed that unused hours roll over fully, with no partial hour forfeiture**, ensuring efficient use of purchased time (18:18)\n    - Colin detailed **188 total hours purchased historically**, with about **180 hours delivered so far**, and a current credit of **22.25 hours** available (19:10).\n    - This rollover enables flexibility during months with fluctuating workload demands.\n    - Yefei emphasized the need to keep the current system stable before engaging in major website projects.\n    - Milan agreed to monitor daily issues to help draw a clear line for system stability.\n\n## **Data Track Integration and Documentation Preparation**\n\nThe team is preparing detailed documentation for a third party building a new POS system to replace Data Track, clarifying integration points and system rationale (04:21).\n\n- **Yefei Jin and Milan Wagner are leading efforts to add context on Data Track’s key features and integration with HubSpot and Aircall**, aiming for delivery by Thursday (11:11)\n    - Milan will add a new section summarizing Data Track’s **top five features**, focusing on sales processing and member check-in functions.\n    - They will document why the team switched from Salesforce and Rank DNA to HubSpot and Aircall, highlighting cost and functionality benefits.\n    - The document will outline the reasons for separating syncs (member status, transactions) and the cost/complexity of each (05:22).\n    - Yefei stressed including in-scope and planned features like e-signature workflows, noting PandaDoc is a temporary workaround.\n\n- **The document will provide a high-level overview first, with technical screenshots and details available upon follow-up requests**, managing client expectations (16:54)\n    - Colin suggested providing screenshots from Make.com to show workflow complexity without overwhelming on initial calls.\n    - Yefei expects Motion IQ to lead the initial meeting and ask questions to clarify integration needs.\n    - The team will prepare to explain the rationale behind multiple syncs and the potential need for APIs.\n    - This approach supports transparent vendor collaboration and informed POS system design.\n\n## **Operational Process Improvements and Team Collaboration**\n\nThe team is focused on refining daily workflows and communication protocols to speed issue resolution and improve system reliability (20:12).\n\n- **Yefei highlighted the need for rapid reporting of issues by gym staff to avoid delays in fixes**, aiming to eliminate core system bugs by December (23:50)\n    - Milan acknowledged that while some occasional breaks occur, the majority of workflows are stable.\n    - Nina clarified that some recent issues stemmed from adding workflows not originally designed for multiple parallel processes.\n    - The team agreed that new feature requests are expected after core stability is reached.\n    - Yefei proposed a goal of one full week without system breakage or urgent questions to mark stability (38:28).\n\n- **Colin and Yefei plan to assist Milan with HubSpot workflow management training**, enabling more autonomous control of marketing lists and campaign adjustments (40:11)\n    - Milan has started exploring HubSpot’s flow pages but has not yet made changes.\n    - Colin assured that workflow editing is straightforward once the necessary contact properties and triggers are understood.\n    - This training will reduce dependency on external support and allow faster mid-month campaign tweaks.\n    - The team will continue collaborating closely on HubSpot and Squarespace tasks to maintain progress.\n\n","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot","SMS Marketing","Data Track","POS System","Workflows","Website Facelift"],"overview":"- **HubSpot Workflow Stabilization:** Core HubSpot system is stabilizing with ongoing fixes for workflow overlaps and lead management. \n\n- **HubSpot Work Priority:** Ongoing HubSpot support remains priority; 10 hours monthly reserved for tweaks and adjustments.\n\n- **Marketing Drip Campaign Progress:** Active drip campaigns have emailed 1,022 leads; re-enrollment for repeat inquiries will resume.\n\n- **SMS Marketing Cost Comparison:** HubSpot SMS feature favored due to lower estimated costs of $600 vs. Aircall’s $1,100.\n\n- **Website Development Plan:** Current site fixes continue while larger WordPress redesign awaits cost and timeline comparison.\n\n- **Data Track Documentation Preparation:** Team documenting Data Track''s features and integration rationale for new POS systems delivery by Thursday.","action_items":"\n**Milan Wagner**\nReview and contribute to the document detailing backend workflows for the POS system rebuild (05:54)\nAdd a section summarizing Data Track key features and issues resolved with HubSpot (14:56)\nAttend the HubSpot rep call, compile detailed questions about SMS integration and platform limitations, and report back (39:16)\nCoordinate with Colin and Nina on HubSpot issues promptly as they arise (43:42)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nAssist in updating the backend workflows document for synchronization scenarios and costs, including screenshots of the make.com system (11:19)\nProvide support for SMS marketing setup, create necessary workflows, and teach Milan how to manage HubSpot flows (40:08)\nDeliver the finalized critical workflows document to Milan and Yefei for onward submission by tomorrow (43:42)\nContinue working on the Squarespace facelift project within current monthly hours (43:42)\n\n**Nina Belina**\nSupport HubSpot workflow troubleshooting and ensure fixes prevent contact list overlaps (07:24)\nProvide technical explanations and collaborate to maintain system stability (20:41)\n\n**Yefei Jin**\nCoordinate the integration of the critical workflows document and oversee communication with Motion IQ (11:19)\nLead discussions on budget allocation for monthly hours, prioritizing HubSpot and SMS implementation within current resources (18:18)\nAdvise on SMS platform evaluation and ensure questions for HubSpot rep are clear and thorough (35:35)\nFacilitate prioritization to reach stable HubSpot system operations and reduce daily issues by end of the month (38:25)\nSupport decision-making on future website redesign projects and budgeting for online store integration (37:18)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"b49755d1-782d-4394-806f-d7038dd3a2d1","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
