    '{"id":"01K98504YTQ8HZDTH79AE00PER","title":"Ricoh // New North: Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Wedding Costs and Planning Insights**\n\nThe discussion highlighted the steep costs and complexity involved in wedding planning, underscoring the need to balance budget and experience effectively.\n\n- **Roz** shared that her wedding for **about 50 people cost around $15,000** (08:57), with venue, food, and decor being major expenses.\n    - She secured a private club venue for **$500 in August and September**, which included tables, chairs, linens, plates, and cutlery (04:20).\n    - The event manager’s exceptional service was critical to a smooth experience, earning a generous tip for her role (11:00).\n    - Unforeseen personal issues arose, such as a family member''s injury and last-minute Covid infections, impacting attendance (06:30).\n    - Roz emphasized the hidden workload in wedding logistics even when the venue is fully equipped (11:28).\n\n- **Lou Bogani** described his brother’s upcoming wedding in **Buenos Aires with 180 guests and a budget over $40,000** (09:16).\n    - The event will feature a relaxed style with food islands and a late-night party, reflecting a more informal reception approach (10:00).\n    - Lou recognized the value of the special moment but questioned the cost-to-duration ratio of weddings (11:54).\n    - He is personally juggling significant wedding prep stress while also planning to attend a major concert the day after (14:00).\n\n- Both Roz and Lou agreed smaller, more intimate weddings or eloping followed by a party could be cost-effective alternatives without losing the celebration’s spirit (12:16).\n    - Roz’s husband preferred a traditional ceremony with details like cake cutting and first dance, illustrating varying expectations that impact planning (13:18).\n\n## **Event Scheduling and Personal Impact**\n\nThe timing of Lou’s brother’s wedding and the adjacent major concert created logistical and personal challenges, affecting resource and energy planning.\n\n- The wedding is scheduled for **Saturday, November 15th**, followed by attending an **Oasis concert at River Plate Stadium with 100,000 attendees** the next day (14:15).\n    - Lou expects the wedding to end around **6 AM**, leaving limited recovery time before heading to the stadium at **4 PM** for the concert starting at **9 PM** (15:56).\n    - He anticipates arriving home around **2 AM the following morning**, risking exhaustion and vocal strain (17:38).\n    - Lou plans to request a **day off on Monday for recovery**, acknowledging the physical toll of back-to-back events (15:46).\n\n- The concert is a major event as part of Oasis’s world tour after a **16-year hiatus since 2009**, with two sold-out shows totaling **approximately 200,000 attendees** (18:30).\n    - The scale and timing of the wedding and concert combination reflect complex personal scheduling challenges for Lou and his family (16:52).\n\n## **Venue and Service Provider Selection**\n\nChoosing the right venue and service providers proved crucial to managing costs and ensuring a quality experience.\n\n- Roz praised the private club’s all-inclusive setup, which reduced vendor coordination by providing furniture, tableware, and kitchen facilities, saving time and complexity (04:20).\n    - The event manager’s hands-on role ensured smooth operations, reducing stress and allowing the couple to focus on the celebration (11:00).\n    - The florist delivered a large quantity of high-quality flowers for **$1,800**, which Roz felt was underpriced given the quality (05:30).\n\n- Lou described his brother’s wedding at a golf club venue with an outdoor tent, emphasizing a relaxed but well-styled atmosphere that fits their budget and guest experience goals (09:30).\n\n## **Product Brochure and Marketing Collateral Progress**\n\nThe team is advancing the Optimizer brochure and related assets with a focus on finalizing content and visuals ahead of critical deadlines.\n\n- **Lou Bogani** committed to completing the Optimizer brochure template today, aiming to deliver it to **Natalie Mintjens by Wednesday** for storyboard review (27:02, 33:02).\n    - He presented new icon options including outlined and solid versions to provide design flexibility for client feedback (28:00).\n    - Roz emphasized the need for content fine-tuning specifically tailored for Optimizer, with a goal to finalize by **December 10th** for the January 10th launch (33:09).\n    - The team is reusing existing icon assets where possible to speed up delivery and maintain consistency (29:40).\n    - Roz asked to retain specific hero image adjustments and content positioning to preserve the intended look and feel (30:35).\n\n- Natalie confirmed receipt of all necessary video and graphic files, enabling ongoing progress on animation and brochure development (27:14, 31:38).\n    - Roz plans to prepare similar collateral for Info Print Manager and RICO Process Director, aiming for early review cycles with product managers (33:53).\n\n## **Market and Event Ticketing Context**\n\nThe conversation revealed frustration around sports event ticket availability and pricing, highlighting challenges in large-scale event accessibility.\n\n- Roz described the **FIFA World Cup ticket situation in Vancouver**, where the largest stadium holds just over **54,000 seats** and premium tickets sell for thousands of dollars, limiting access (19:51).\n    - She criticized FIFA’s pricing and early ticketing practices as a cash grab, echoing dissatisfaction with similar issues in other markets (20:30).\n    - Lou noted that high demand is driven by star players like **Messi**, especially as this might be his last World Cup, increasing pressure on ticket sales in Miami and Argentina (21:00).\n    - Roz explained a recent incident where Messi did not attend a promoted event in Vancouver, causing public outrage and accusations of false advertising (22:30).\n    - Both Roz and Nathalie shared examples of fan disappointment and frustration in Hong Kong and Vancouver due to incomplete player appearances at matches (23:00).\n\n- The team watched the Netflix documentary **FIFA Uncovered**, confirming widespread corruption and financial motives behind FIFA’s operations, which further erodes fan trust (25:20).\n\n## **Team Coordination and Deadlines**\n\nClear deadlines and collaborative coordination are driving the final stages of the Optimizer launch preparations.\n\n- Roz’s meeting with the product manager is set for **Wednesday at 10 AM**, requiring an updated brochure draft beforehand to secure approval (33:00).\n    - Lou is prioritizing final icon adjustments, balloon design arcs, and hero image fixes to meet this deadline (30:28).\n    - Roz is actively preparing content for additional product brochures, signaling a broader refresh initiative within marketing collateral (33:50).\n    - Natalie is tasked with integrating all assets and ensuring files are ready for animation and final edits (31:38).\n    - The launch timeline demands all materials be finalized by **December 10th**, supporting the **January 10th Optimizer product launch** (33:09).","outline":null,"keywords":["wedding planning","event management","Optimizer brochure","world cup tickets","Oasis concert","FIFA corruption"],"overview":"- **Wedding Costs:** Roz’s wedding for 50 guests cost $15,000; venue, food, and decor were major expenses.  \n- **Brother''s Wedding:** Lou''s brother’s wedding in Buenos Aires will host 180 guests with a budget over $40,000.  \n- **Event Scheduling:** Lou faces challenges planning his brother''s wedding on November 15th, followed by an Oasis concert the next day.  \n- **Venue Selection:** All-inclusive venues simplify logistics; Roz praised her private club for reducing vendor coordination.  \n- **Ticketing Challenges:** FIFA World Cup tickets in Vancouver are expensive and limited; demand rises with star players like Messi.  \n- **Project Deadlines:** The Optimizer launch requires all materials finalized by December 10th for a January 10th release.","action_items":"\n**Lou Bogani**\nFinalize and deliver the Optimizer/template brochure by end of day (27:36)\nProvide both outline and solid versions of new icons for selection by Linea (27:43)\n\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nPrepare storyboard for the upcoming video by Wednesday (27:02)\n\n**Roz Regan**\nSubmit rough content drafts of brochures for Info Print Manager and RICO Process Director to team for further refinement (34:58)\nShare finalized brochure copy with product manager by Friday meeting for sign-off (27:36)\n"},"duration":35.38999938964844,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Roz"},{"id":1,"name":"Lou Bogani"},{"id":2,"name":"Nathalie Mintjens"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":18.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":18.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"How are we doing this morning or.","index":1,"end_time":21.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":19.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, this afternoon, I guess, for you guys?","index":2,"end_time":23.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":21.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, good.","index":3,"end_time":25.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":24.4,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"These crazy days for me.","index":4,"end_time":27.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":25.77,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":5,"end_time":31.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":30.81,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"My brother.","index":6,"end_time":31.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":31.29,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"My brother is getting married.","index":7,"end_time":33.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":31.81,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, so it is crazy then.","index":8,"end_time":35.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":33.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":9,"end_time":36.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":36.33,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Going like, to test the suit.","index":10,"end_time":41.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":37.85,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Helping my brother with some arrangements.","index":11,"end_time":45.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":42.49,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"My mother is going crazy.","index":12,"end_time":48.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":46.57,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"My father is going crazy.","index":13,"end_time":49.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":48.05,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":14,"end_time":55.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":53.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, it''s been a couple of rough and crazy days, so.","index":15,"end_time":62.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":57.06,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, my.","index":16,"end_time":62.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":62.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I feel you.","index":17,"end_time":63.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"My husband and I, we just got married a year ago, and bless his.","index":18,"end_time":70.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":63.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Bless his heart, he had no clue what he was getting into.","index":19,"end_time":74.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":70.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I said to him, I''m like, we please elope.","index":20,"end_time":78.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":76.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, legit.","index":21,"end_time":79.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":78.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he''s like, what?","index":22,"end_time":80.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":79.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, yeah, no, legitimately, I would much rather spend all this money going somewhere really cool with you and getting married there with, like, no one than doing.","index":23,"end_time":88.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":80.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s like.","index":24,"end_time":88.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":88.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s like, no.","index":25,"end_time":89.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":88.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, he''s got a.","index":26,"end_time":90.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":89.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s got a family, and he''s the last kid to get married out of three of them.","index":27,"end_time":94.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":90.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, you know, like, so there was a lot of family involved.","index":28,"end_time":97.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":94.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And.","index":29,"end_time":97.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":97.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he was like, no.","index":30,"end_time":99.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":98.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He goes, I really.","index":31,"end_time":100.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":99.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was very clear.","index":32,"end_time":100.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":100.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I have to hand it to him.","index":33,"end_time":101.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":100.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s always very clear about what he likes and what he doesn''t like.","index":34,"end_time":104.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":101.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he was like, no.","index":35,"end_time":105.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":104.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He goes, I really want to do it.","index":36,"end_time":106.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":105.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, okay.","index":37,"end_time":107.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":106.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he''s like, well, can we keep it small at least?","index":38,"end_time":109.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":107.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, yeah, absolutely.","index":39,"end_time":110.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":109.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So in my mind, I''m like, we''re at, like, 45, 50 people with just immediate family and very close friends.","index":40,"end_time":117.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":111.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he''s like, well, there''s only, like, five of us in my family.","index":41,"end_time":121.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":117.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, hon, sweetheart, I''m like, your sisters are married.","index":42,"end_time":126.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":121.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he''s like, huh?","index":43,"end_time":127.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":126.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And they both have two kids.","index":44,"end_time":128.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":127.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he''s like, yeah.","index":45,"end_time":130.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":128.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, that''s 10 people right there.","index":46,"end_time":133.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":130.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he''s like, oh.","index":47,"end_time":134.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":133.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, It.","index":48,"end_time":138.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":137.43,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It adds up a lot.","index":49,"end_time":139.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":138.31,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, quickly.","index":50,"end_time":140.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":139.51,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":51,"end_time":142.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":140.71,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"My brother was.","index":52,"end_time":143.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":142.79,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"My brother was like, telling me, or like, the.","index":53,"end_time":146.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":144.47,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"The people that it was like, there''s going to be attending the wedding.","index":54,"end_time":150.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":146.95,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Just like that.","index":55,"end_time":152.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":151.59,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It was like 180 people, like, yeah, already.","index":56,"end_time":156.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":152.31,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And it was like, just quickly, like, counting friends, family, close friends from the.","index":57,"end_time":162.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":156.23,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"From the room.","index":58,"end_time":163.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.86,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, it was like, yeah, yeah, like that.","index":59,"end_time":166.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":164.02,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s.","index":60,"end_time":167.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":166.98,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We.","index":61,"end_time":168.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":167.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We ended up at about 45, 50 people, I think, at the end of the day, which is for.","index":62,"end_time":173.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":168.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"For.","index":63,"end_time":174.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":173.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Unlike.","index":64,"end_time":174.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":174.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If only it could be smaller.","index":65,"end_time":176.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":174.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, seriously, if only it could be smaller.","index":66,"end_time":178.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":176.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he was like, again, bless his heart.","index":67,"end_time":182.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":178.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s like, how expensive could it possibly be?","index":68,"end_time":185.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":182.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, oh, you have no idea.","index":69,"end_time":187.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":185.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we.","index":70,"end_time":191.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":191.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, I think the light bulb went on when we were looking for a venue.","index":71,"end_time":196.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":192.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, you know, 50 people''s not big.","index":72,"end_time":198.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":196.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that''s easy to accommodate, you know, in a.","index":73,"end_time":202.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":199.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"In Vancouver, because, you know, it''s not like New York or Chicago or.","index":74,"end_time":207.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":202.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Or la, where you''ve got like a.","index":75,"end_time":208.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":207.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, you have places where you can put like 300 people if you need to.","index":76,"end_time":213.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":208.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Vancouver''s the much smaller.","index":77,"end_time":214.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":213.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And so we were looking at, like, places that were like an hour and a half outside of downtown even.","index":78,"end_time":222.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":214.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And just to walk through the door was like $5,000.","index":79,"end_time":225.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":222.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, just.","index":80,"end_time":225.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":225.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s just to use the space, right?","index":81,"end_time":227.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":225.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, I used to be an event manager, so I''m like, no, that''s not happening.","index":82,"end_time":231.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":227.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s ridiculous.","index":83,"end_time":234.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":233.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, one place downtown, and it was a small restaurant to do a buyout of the restaurant was going to be $15,000.","index":84,"end_time":242.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, it''s a lot of money.","index":85,"end_time":245.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":244.05,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, oh, yeah, it''s ridiculous.","index":86,"end_time":248.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":245.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was ridiculous.","index":87,"end_time":249.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":248.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, funnily enough, one of the places that I just sent an email to just kind of like, it was.","index":88,"end_time":256.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":249.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I thought it was going to be like a throwaway.","index":89,"end_time":257.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":256.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I thought, oh, it''s going to be really expensive because it''s a private club.","index":90,"end_time":261.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":258.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But they were doing some kind of.","index":91,"end_time":264.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":262.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They were looking for the revenue, and they were like, we''re having a deal right now for the months of August and September.","index":92,"end_time":272.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":264.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it was $500.","index":93,"end_time":273.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":272.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that $500, which I thought was totally fair, included all the tables, the chairs, the linens, the plates, the cutlery, like, everything you.","index":94,"end_time":284.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":274.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You need for a reception and the room.","index":95,"end_time":287.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And they have a full.","index":96,"end_time":289.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":288.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Had a full kitchen there as well.","index":97,"end_time":291.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":289.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So all the food was done.","index":98,"end_time":293.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":292.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the food was excellent because it''s a private club.","index":99,"end_time":295.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":293.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was really, really good.","index":100,"end_time":296.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":295.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I was like, well.","index":101,"end_time":299.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":296.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the event manager there was spectacular.","index":102,"end_time":302.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":299.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"She was so good.","index":103,"end_time":304.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":302.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I said to.","index":104,"end_time":305.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":304.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I said to Charlie, I''m like, I don''t need to look at anything more.","index":105,"end_time":307.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":305.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This will work just fine for me.","index":106,"end_time":309.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":307.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he was like, yeah, no, he goes, I got a really good feel.","index":107,"end_time":312.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":309.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we wound up doing it at this private club, a beautiful room with a balcony.","index":108,"end_time":318.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":312.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, you know, we opened up the balcony to everyone because it was the summer.","index":109,"end_time":321.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":318.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And yeah, it was.","index":110,"end_time":322.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":321.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It went really, really well.","index":111,"end_time":324.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":322.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":112,"end_time":324.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":324.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the only people we needed to bring in were the dj, the photographer, the florist, and justice of the peace, because that''s how we did it.","index":113,"end_time":332.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":324.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re not religious, so it was just a civil ceremony, and that was it.","index":114,"end_time":336.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":332.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the justice of the peace lived across the street.","index":115,"end_time":338.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":336.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So literally, she walked across the street and did our thing and walked home.","index":116,"end_time":341.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":338.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, okay.","index":117,"end_time":342.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":341.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''S awesome.","index":118,"end_time":345.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":344.69,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":119,"end_time":346.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":345.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the florist, I was blown away.","index":120,"end_time":348.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":346.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, he showed up with, like, two huge wire racks full of flowers, and I was like, oh, my God.","index":121,"end_time":355.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":348.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he only charged, like, 1800 bucks for it all.","index":122,"end_time":358.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":355.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I was like, dude, you need to be start charging, like, literally double for this.","index":123,"end_time":362.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":358.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":124,"end_time":363.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":362.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So everything at the end of the day sort of worked out.","index":125,"end_time":366.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":364.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s.","index":126,"end_time":368.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":367.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s always the things that you can''t do anything about.","index":127,"end_time":370.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":368.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like his.","index":128,"end_time":371.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":370.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"My.","index":129,"end_time":371.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":371.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"My husband''s mom, like, two, three months before the wedding, slipped and fell and broke her leg.","index":130,"end_time":377.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":371.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So she was in a wheel.","index":131,"end_time":380.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":379.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, so she was in a wheelchair.","index":132,"end_time":381.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":380.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then his older sister and her entire family got Covid and couldn''t come.","index":133,"end_time":387.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":381.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know, right?","index":134,"end_time":389.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":388.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''m like, got one of my really good friends to FaceTime her so that they could at least see the ceremony and speeches and stuff like that.","index":135,"end_time":398.709,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":390.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But, yeah, they couldn''t make it.","index":136,"end_time":399.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":398.709,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, they''re.","index":137,"end_time":400.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":399.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They''re in California.","index":138,"end_time":402.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":400.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So they''re like, well, they won''t let us on a plane.","index":139,"end_time":404.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":402.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, no.","index":140,"end_time":405.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":404.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, and please don''t come.","index":141,"end_time":406.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":405.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because they won''t let you in.","index":142,"end_time":409.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":406.67,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"They were really sick, right?","index":143,"end_time":410.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":409.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, they were really sick.","index":144,"end_time":411.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":410.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And they said, well, we can get in a car and drive up.","index":145,"end_time":414.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":411.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, I can''t think of anything more miserable, frankly.","index":146,"end_time":418.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":414.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re sick with three other people who are equally as sick stuck in a car for a day.","index":147,"end_time":423.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":418.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, that''s bad.","index":148,"end_time":425.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":423.11,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":149,"end_time":426.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":425.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So Charlie called me in the middle of the day from work, which he never does, and he tells me this, and I''m like, no, I don''t.","index":150,"end_time":432.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":426.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, it''s going to sound really horrible.","index":151,"end_time":434.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":432.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I said it to him, but I''m like, I don''t want them to come because that just sounds like a misery to me.","index":152,"end_time":437.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":434.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I would.","index":153,"end_time":438.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I would rather shoot myself in the face, literally, than get in a car for, like, a day to drive from California to Vancouver while really, really sick.","index":154,"end_time":448.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":439.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, no.","index":155,"end_time":449.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":449.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"How much is it?","index":156,"end_time":451.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":450.34,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like eight hours, kind of.","index":157,"end_time":452.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":451.3,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh.","index":158,"end_time":453.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":452.78,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, no.","index":159,"end_time":453.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":453.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re talking, like, they usually take two days to do the drive.","index":160,"end_time":457.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":453.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, they usually stop, like, in Oregon or somewhere.","index":161,"end_time":460.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":457.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, it''s.","index":162,"end_time":461.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":460.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s.","index":163,"end_time":462.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":461.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s.","index":164,"end_time":462.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":462.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s.","index":165,"end_time":463.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":462.78,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s a drive.","index":166,"end_time":463.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":463.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a drive.","index":167,"end_time":465.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":463.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s yeah, like 15 hours, 16 hours, something like that.","index":168,"end_time":469.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":465.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I want to say.","index":169,"end_time":470.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":469.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, like, it''s not just, oh, it''s a couple hours, come on over.","index":170,"end_time":472.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":470.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, no, it''s.","index":171,"end_time":474.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":472.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a lot.","index":172,"end_time":476.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":475.63,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a lot.","index":173,"end_time":478.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":477.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I feel your pain because we just went through it and I''m just like, oh, my God, why didn''t we allow.","index":174,"end_time":482.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":478.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m stressing out and I''m not even the one that''s getting married.","index":175,"end_time":487.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":483.71,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I''m.","index":176,"end_time":487.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":487.07,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I''m like that.","index":177,"end_time":488.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":487.39,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And I took like this moment to a pre because my younger brother, and he''s getting married, like, before me.","index":178,"end_time":495.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":488.19,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I''m not married yet.","index":179,"end_time":496.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":495.37,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And I was.","index":180,"end_time":497.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":496.57,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I was like, okay, this is really cool experience from when I get married.","index":181,"end_time":500.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":497.17,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, I know there''s a lot of information to grab from this.","index":182,"end_time":506.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":501.05,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, you have no idea.","index":183,"end_time":508.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Trust me.","index":184,"end_time":508.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":508.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The bride is buffering you because she''s got it in her head what she wants.","index":185,"end_time":512.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":508.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You have no clue.","index":186,"end_time":513.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":512.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Alop.","index":187,"end_time":514.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":513.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Trust me.","index":188,"end_time":515.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":514.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just a lobe.","index":189,"end_time":515.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":515.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"First he has to find a wife.","index":190,"end_time":518.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":517.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That''S willing to elope.","index":191,"end_time":520.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":518.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":192,"end_time":520.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":520.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Honestly, if he had said yes, we would have just run off, like, to Scotland or something.","index":193,"end_time":530.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":525.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, I was.","index":194,"end_time":531.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":530.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was all in for that because weddings are so expensive.","index":195,"end_time":534.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":531.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, it was only like 50 people.","index":196,"end_time":536.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":534.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":197,"end_time":537.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":536.8,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And it still cost us 15 grand.","index":198,"end_time":539.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":537.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, with everything right, like, the food, the bar, the venue, like the, like, just.","index":199,"end_time":545.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":540.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It all starts to really add up.","index":200,"end_time":547.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":545.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, we were somewhere in like, like 15, 14 to 15,000 for everything.","index":201,"end_time":552.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":547.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that was only 50 people.","index":202,"end_time":554.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":553.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So can you imagine?","index":203,"end_time":556,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":554.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, my bro, my brother is kind of in that.","index":204,"end_time":560.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":556.64,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, I think he''s spending above, like, 40 grand.","index":205,"end_time":564.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":560.64,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, @ least.","index":206,"end_time":565.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":564.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":207,"end_time":566.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":565.36,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"For that many people.","index":208,"end_time":567.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":566.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":209,"end_time":568.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":567.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that many people.","index":210,"end_time":569.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":568.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And where is it, like, geographically?","index":211,"end_time":570.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":569.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, it''s like in Buenos Aires.","index":212,"end_time":574.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":570.88,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":213,"end_time":575.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":575.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s like.","index":214,"end_time":577.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":576.46,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s like a golf club.","index":215,"end_time":578.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":577.5,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s really nice.","index":216,"end_time":579.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":579.1,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, the place is really, really amazing.","index":217,"end_time":581.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":579.98,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And it''s going to be like all outside with the tent and all that.","index":218,"end_time":585.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":582.62,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, this like, new style of like, kind of.","index":219,"end_time":590.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":586.14,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I would say not.","index":220,"end_time":593.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":591.34,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s going to be all formally dressed, but it''s like kind of know how to explain it, but more relaxed style of like wedding.","index":221,"end_time":600.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":593.26,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, it''s like, like small, like, seating area or like it.","index":222,"end_time":605.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":600.63,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It isn''t like formal.","index":223,"end_time":606.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":605.91,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, at this time we.","index":224,"end_time":608.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":606.99,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We have dinner.","index":225,"end_time":609.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":608.71,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"At this time we dance.","index":226,"end_time":610.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":609.51,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s like the reception.","index":227,"end_time":612.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":610.47,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"The reception.","index":228,"end_time":612.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":612.07,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Reception.","index":229,"end_time":613.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":613.19,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Then we have like the, like some food islands with different type of food, like Asian, like Argentinian barbecue and all stuff.","index":230,"end_time":622.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":613.91,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And then we have, like, after 12, it''s like, dance up until, like, the party''s over.","index":231,"end_time":626.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":622.39,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So it''s like, it''s going to be, like, a really, really fun.","index":232,"end_time":630.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":626.83,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"But as I told you, it''s really good insight to what.","index":233,"end_time":634.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":630.79,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I don''t want to spend all that money for, like, six hours of.","index":234,"end_time":638.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":634.75,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":235,"end_time":640.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":639.51,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Right.","index":236,"end_time":640.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":640.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And there''s a lot of moving parts, too.","index":237,"end_time":643.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":640.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, especially if you have a venue where you have to bring everything in, like the tables and chairs and all the rest of it.","index":238,"end_time":649.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":643.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that''s what Charlie and I really loved about our venue was that they had all of these things.","index":239,"end_time":653.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":649.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We didn''t have to, you know, coordinate ordering in because it was all there.","index":240,"end_time":659.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":653.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":241,"end_time":660.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":660.09,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And like I said, everything hinged on the.","index":242,"end_time":663.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":660.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The event manager that we had.","index":243,"end_time":664.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":663.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And she was really good.","index":244,"end_time":667.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":664.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, really good.","index":245,"end_time":668.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":667.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I mean it.","index":246,"end_time":670.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":669.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, we tipped her out quite well at the end because she was.","index":247,"end_time":673.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":670.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"She was just that good.","index":248,"end_time":674.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":673.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, I mean, we would have tipped anyway, but I was just.","index":249,"end_time":677.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":674.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"She made it smooth.","index":250,"end_time":679.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":678.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I think that that was, like, the one thing that I was.","index":251,"end_time":682.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":679.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I didn''t feel like I had to worry about anything because I knew she was there.","index":252,"end_time":686.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":682.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":253,"end_time":687.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":687.53,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":254,"end_time":688.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":687.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":255,"end_time":688.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":688.37,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And I sung her praises to her gm, who popped his head in when we were just doing a little bit of, you know, a little bit of decorating, just waiting for the florist and that kind of thing.","index":256,"end_time":696.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":688.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And just.","index":257,"end_time":698.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":696.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There''s just.","index":258,"end_time":699.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":698.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Even when you''ve got a venue where you''ve got everything come already there, it''s still a lot of moving parts.","index":259,"end_time":704.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":699.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, it''s still a lot of people and.","index":260,"end_time":707.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":704.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I just elope.","index":261,"end_time":709.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":707.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"My friend.","index":262,"end_time":710.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":709.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Save the money, Buy a house, Go on vacation.","index":263,"end_time":713.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":710.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, we were talking with my girlfriend, like.","index":264,"end_time":717.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":714.37,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, it''s.","index":265,"end_time":720.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":717.81,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I mean, I would.","index":266,"end_time":721.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":720.45,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I will not say that it''s not worth it because it''s.","index":267,"end_time":723.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":721.45,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s really a really special moment with all the family and friends and all the people you love.","index":268,"end_time":727.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":723.49,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"But I''m like, I don''t know if I want to spend that amount of money in, like, a bunch of hours, like a couple of hours.","index":269,"end_time":734.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":727.81,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s not.","index":270,"end_time":735.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":735.17,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I.","index":271,"end_time":736.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":735.73,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So here''s what you do, is you go and you elope, and then you come back and you just have a party.","index":272,"end_time":741.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":736.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":273,"end_time":742.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":742.3,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":274,"end_time":743.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":742.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, you just have, like, a party, a dinner or whatever.","index":275,"end_time":747.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":743.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":276,"end_time":747.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":747.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because that''s really the fun part about a wedding.","index":277,"end_time":749.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":747.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s always.","index":278,"end_time":750.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":749.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s always after everything''s done, right?","index":279,"end_time":751.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":750.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Food and dancing.","index":280,"end_time":752.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":751.78,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, food and dancing.","index":281,"end_time":753.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":752.46,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":282,"end_time":753.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":753.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Food and dancing.","index":283,"end_time":754.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":753.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Have a party.","index":284,"end_time":757.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":756.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":285,"end_time":757.819,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":757.339,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":286,"end_time":759.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":758.7,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I think we''re Gonna do that?","index":287,"end_time":760.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":759.66,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, that''s, like.","index":288,"end_time":761.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":760.74,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I would have done it that way if.","index":289,"end_time":763.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":762.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If my husband would have been all in.","index":290,"end_time":765.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":763.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But he was.","index":291,"end_time":765.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":765.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was quite funny.","index":292,"end_time":766.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":765.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He was quite traditional.","index":293,"end_time":767.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":766.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He was like.","index":294,"end_time":768.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":767.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He wanted, like, the cake cutting and the first dance and all the rest of it.","index":295,"end_time":772.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":769.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Blossom''s Heart.","index":296,"end_time":773.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":772.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m just like, oh, God.","index":297,"end_time":774.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":773.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":298,"end_time":774.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":774.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was the one.","index":299,"end_time":775.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":774.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He was the.","index":300,"end_time":776.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":775.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He was the.","index":301,"end_time":777.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":776.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He was like, more the bride than I was, because I was like, I just want to put on a pretty dress and marry you.","index":302,"end_time":782.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":777.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, I don''t give a shit if this, like, this place burns down.","index":303,"end_time":785.009,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":782.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just as long as the end of the day, you and I are married.","index":304,"end_time":786.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":785.009,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s all I care about.","index":305,"end_time":787.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":786.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, yeah, like, this.","index":306,"end_time":789.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":787.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Literally, this entire thing could, like, flop.","index":307,"end_time":792.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":789.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And as long as you and I are married at the end of the day, that''s really all I care about.","index":308,"end_time":795.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":792.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Makes sense.","index":309,"end_time":798.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":797.68,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":310,"end_time":798.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":798.04,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":311,"end_time":799.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":798.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So he was way more like the whole cake cutting thing and the, you know, he.","index":312,"end_time":803.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":799.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He was very specific about the suit he wanted and.","index":313,"end_time":806.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":803.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the flowers and, like.","index":314,"end_time":808.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":806.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, he was way more into the detail, funnily enough, I think, than I was.","index":315,"end_time":812.079,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":808.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was just there to make his vision happen.","index":316,"end_time":814.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":812.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re a rare one, Roz.","index":317,"end_time":818.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":816.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I love him.","index":318,"end_time":819.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":818.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was so funny.","index":319,"end_time":822.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":820.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was just like, really?","index":320,"end_time":823.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":822.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he was like.","index":321,"end_time":824.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":823.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, I thought guys didn''t care about this kind of crap.","index":322,"end_time":826.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":824.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he''s like, no, no.","index":323,"end_time":827.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":826.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He goes, I want to do the first dance with you.","index":324,"end_time":829.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":827.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He.","index":325,"end_time":830.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":829.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, and we took lessons and everything.","index":326,"end_time":832.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":830.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, he was.","index":327,"end_time":833.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":832.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It wasn''t like he was just saying it.","index":328,"end_time":835.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":833.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He was all in.","index":329,"end_time":837.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":835.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was like, okay, Yeah.","index":330,"end_time":843.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":837.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I love him.","index":331,"end_time":844.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":843.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s so adorable.","index":332,"end_time":845.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":844.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, dear.","index":333,"end_time":849.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":848.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But what.","index":334,"end_time":850.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":850.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So when did they get married, though?","index":335,"end_time":851.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":850.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, soon.","index":336,"end_time":852.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":851.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Will the craziness be over soon?","index":337,"end_time":854.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":852.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s actually next Saturday.","index":338,"end_time":857.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":855.46,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, wow.","index":339,"end_time":858.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":857.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":340,"end_time":858.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":858.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So you''re coming up on it then?","index":341,"end_time":860.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":858.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":342,"end_time":861.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":860.5,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s like, not like this Saturday is coming, but then it''s the 15th.","index":343,"end_time":865.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":861.3,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like.","index":344,"end_time":865.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":865.22,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":345,"end_time":868.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":867.46,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So it''s.","index":346,"end_time":868.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":868.38,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s kind of a crazy, like, time also because on the next day, we''re going to see Oasis.","index":347,"end_time":875.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":868.78,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"That.","index":348,"end_time":876.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":875.87,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So it''s.","index":349,"end_time":877.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":877.39,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We''re gonna.","index":350,"end_time":878.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":877.91,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We''re gonna be so hangover.","index":351,"end_time":879.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":878.47,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, it''s gonna be crazy.","index":352,"end_time":881.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":879.63,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And we have to go to a.","index":353,"end_time":882.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":881.35,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, I don''t know how many hours they''re gonna play, but it''s crazy.","index":354,"end_time":888.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":882.63,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Muffin.","index":355,"end_time":889.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":888.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, have no sympathy for you whatsoever.","index":356,"end_time":893.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":890.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, when.","index":357,"end_time":895.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":893.15,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"When we heard about.","index":358,"end_time":896.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":895.19,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So we.","index":359,"end_time":896.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":896.03,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We.","index":360,"end_time":896.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":896.55,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We purchased the tickets before knowing the date, and I was like, oh, fuck.","index":361,"end_time":902.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":896.91,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Because we are all going.","index":362,"end_time":904.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":903.47,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"My brother.","index":363,"end_time":905.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":904.59,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"The.","index":364,"end_time":905.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":905.19,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"The the her, his future wife, my girlfriend, myself, my father, a bunch of friends.","index":365,"end_time":912.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":905.51,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So it''s going to be like a whole caravan of people going to the gig.","index":366,"end_time":915.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":912.3,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s going to be fun, but we''re going to be like zombies going to the.","index":367,"end_time":919.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":916.86,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We''re going to be like, drink water, my friend.","index":368,"end_time":923.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":920.78,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"That''s all I got for you.","index":369,"end_time":925.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":923.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We are definitely going into, like, water treatment.","index":370,"end_time":928.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":925.5,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We''re going to, like, a blowout wedding with, like, 200 people, and then the next night we''re going to see Oasis.","index":371,"end_time":936.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":931.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Good luck.","index":372,"end_time":937.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":937.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s what we were thinking.","index":373,"end_time":940.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":939.05,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, good luck to us because it''s going to be hard.","index":374,"end_time":942.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":940.45,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"May the odds be ever in your favor, as they say.","index":375,"end_time":945.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":942.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was.","index":376,"end_time":947.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":946.57,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I listen, I was like, just thinking about asking for the day off on Monday.","index":377,"end_time":952.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":947.05,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":378,"end_time":954.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":953.77,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"For recovery.","index":379,"end_time":955.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":954.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, just for recovery.","index":380,"end_time":957.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":956.01,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Because, like, so the wedding ends at, like, 5 in the morning, 6am in the morning, kind of.","index":381,"end_time":964.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":957.81,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So.","index":382,"end_time":964.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":964.84,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Because here in Argentina, we kind of hard parties.","index":383,"end_time":967.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":964.96,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":384,"end_time":968.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":967.96,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We have this, like, great schedule of, like, parties and.","index":385,"end_time":971.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":968.36,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And going out.","index":386,"end_time":972.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":971.92,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So the party is at like, 6am and we have to wake up kind of 12, like 12 in the midday because we have to get to the.","index":387,"end_time":984.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":973.24,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"To the stadium at like, 4.","index":388,"end_time":987.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":985,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh.","index":389,"end_time":988.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":987.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it''s kind of.","index":390,"end_time":990.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":989.08,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s kind of one hour from our house and we have to find the parking spot, walk over there, get into the stadium.","index":391,"end_time":997.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":990.46,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And Oasis like, starts at 9 in the.","index":392,"end_time":1000.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":997.46,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"In the.","index":393,"end_time":1001.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1000.94,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"In the night.","index":394,"end_time":1002.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1001.38,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And it''s going to end up four.","index":395,"end_time":1004.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1002.38,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":396,"end_time":1005.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1005.18,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s going to be crazy.","index":397,"end_time":1006.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1005.54,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like River Plate Stadium.","index":398,"end_time":1007.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1006.34,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s going to be like 100k people, like, getting into the city.","index":399,"end_time":1012.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1008.06,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh.","index":400,"end_time":1012.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1012.38,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Because it''s just.","index":401,"end_time":1013.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1012.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just so many people.","index":402,"end_time":1015.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1013.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, I see.","index":403,"end_time":1015.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1015.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":404,"end_time":1016.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1015.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":405,"end_time":1017.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1016.34,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We don''t do.","index":406,"end_time":1018.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1017.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We don''t do concerts that big up here.","index":407,"end_time":1020.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1018.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We just.","index":408,"end_time":1021.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1020.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, I''m sure we could, but we just don''t have any place to put that many people, Honestly, like, sincerely.","index":409,"end_time":1027.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1021.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":410,"end_time":1028.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1027.88,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So, yeah, Oasis starts at nine, is going to play for around two hours, kind of, from what I''ve seen on the.","index":411,"end_time":1035.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1029.12,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"On the.","index":412,"end_time":1035.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1035.28,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"The tour.","index":413,"end_time":1036.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1035.68,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"The world tour that they''re doing.","index":414,"end_time":1037.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1036.08,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":415,"end_time":1038.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1037.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we''re going to end.","index":416,"end_time":1039.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1038.04,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s going to end up like 11, and then we have to get out of the stadium.","index":417,"end_time":1043.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1039.04,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"That''s usually takes half an hour, kind of 40 minutes to all the people to get out, go to the car, get back home.","index":418,"end_time":1049.709,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1043.28,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So I got it.","index":419,"end_time":1050.749,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1049.869,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"We''re probably going to end up, like, reaching my bed at like, 2:00am, kind of.","index":420,"end_time":1055.949,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1050.749,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I was going to say, like one or two at least.","index":421,"end_time":1058.269,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1055.949,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, at least.","index":422,"end_time":1059.469,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1058.269,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And.","index":423,"end_time":1060.189,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1059.789,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And taking into account all the weight from the.","index":424,"end_time":1063.149,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1060.269,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"From the previous day is going to be, like, really, really rough.","index":425,"end_time":1067.549,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1063.629,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It is what it is.","index":426,"end_time":1070.509,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1069.389,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"At least we''re going without with a lot of people, like friends, so it''s going to be a bit more like.","index":427,"end_time":1075.469,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1070.509,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I can''t wait to hear how this all goes down for you.","index":428,"end_time":1078.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1076,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I. I think I''m going to be without any voice next Thursday.","index":429,"end_time":1082.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1080.16,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I''m gonna be like.","index":430,"end_time":1083.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1082.8,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I''m going to be like this.","index":431,"end_time":1084.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1083.6,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I''m going to be with, like, my boy is going to get, like, destroyed.","index":432,"end_time":1090.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1086,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oasis seems really random.","index":433,"end_time":1092.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1090.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I didn''t even know they were touring.","index":434,"end_time":1093.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1092.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, they''re doing a full world tour, reunion stuff.","index":435,"end_time":1097.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1094.56,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Because they were like.","index":436,"end_time":1098.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1097.64,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Is that what it is?","index":437,"end_time":1099.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1098.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, they were.","index":438,"end_time":1100.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1099.68,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"They would.","index":439,"end_time":1100.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1100.52,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"They split up for, like, 60 years.","index":440,"end_time":1102.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1100.92,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s what I thought that song was like Oasis.","index":441,"end_time":1106.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1103.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What?","index":442,"end_time":1106.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1106.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, I didn''t even realize they were back.","index":443,"end_time":1109.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1106.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, no, you''re right.","index":444,"end_time":1110.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1109.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":445,"end_time":1110.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1110.5,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Last time they were in Argentina, In Argentina was 2009, actually, and it was in River Place Stadium.","index":446,"end_time":1117.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1110.9,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And now they are coming again after 16 years and they sold out.","index":447,"end_time":1121.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1117.1,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So there''s like.","index":448,"end_time":1123.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1122.5,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And they''ve got, like.","index":449,"end_time":1125.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1123.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So they''ve got November 15, November 16, then they go over to Chile and then they''re back to.","index":450,"end_time":1131.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1125.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"To Brazil and then.","index":451,"end_time":1132.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1131.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Brazil.","index":452,"end_time":1133.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1132.63,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Brazil, yeah.","index":453,"end_time":1134.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1133.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Wow.","index":454,"end_time":1134.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1134.15,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":455,"end_time":1134.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1134.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":456,"end_time":1135.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1135.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And they''re coming from Australia, too.","index":457,"end_time":1138.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1136.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Wow.","index":458,"end_time":1138.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1138.03,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Okay.","index":459,"end_time":1138.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1138.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":460,"end_time":1140.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1139.51,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s full tour and they are, like, really, really, like, expecting this gig.","index":461,"end_time":1146.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1140.07,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, if you go to, like, some interviews that they were, like, doing to n. They were like, we want to get to Argentina.","index":462,"end_time":1153.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1146.67,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Because last time was.","index":463,"end_time":1154.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1153.35,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Was really special and it''s a lot of people.","index":464,"end_time":1157.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1154.87,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, it''s like almost 200 people between the two dates.","index":465,"end_time":1159.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1157.07,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So.","index":466,"end_time":1160.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1159.91,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"200k.","index":467,"end_time":1160.834,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1160.15,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"200,000 people.","index":468,"end_time":1161.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1160.986,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"200.","index":469,"end_time":1162.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1161.95,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Well, yeah.","index":470,"end_time":1163.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1163.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a lot.","index":471,"end_time":1164.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1163.49,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s not.","index":472,"end_time":1165.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1164.45,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"That''s crazy.","index":473,"end_time":1166.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1165.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s so many people.","index":474,"end_time":1167.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1166.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t even know put that many people in Vancouver.","index":475,"end_time":1170.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1167.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Seriously.","index":476,"end_time":1170.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1170.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, we just don''t have, you know, because.","index":477,"end_time":1173.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1171.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, so here''s the thing, right?","index":478,"end_time":1175.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1174.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Is that we have.","index":479,"end_time":1176.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1175.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We have FIFA coming to.","index":480,"end_time":1178.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1176.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, it''s coming to Vancouver and Toronto and Canada a bunch.","index":481,"end_time":1182.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1178.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":482,"end_time":1183.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1183.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The World Cup, a bunch of places in.","index":483,"end_time":1184.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1183.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"In the States and then a bunch of places.","index":484,"end_time":1186.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1184.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I want to say in Mexico.","index":485,"end_time":1188.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1186.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, Mexico used on the States.","index":486,"end_time":1190.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1188.78,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":487,"end_time":1191.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1190.1,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And so just to give you an idea, like, to get tickets for Vancouver, they haven''t.","index":488,"end_time":1197.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1191.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They''re either.","index":489,"end_time":1198.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1197.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m still a little fuzzy.","index":490,"end_time":1200.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1198.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They''re either already sold out and they haven''t even put them to the public yet or if you want tickets for it.","index":491,"end_time":1207.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1200.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because this, the biggest stadium we have is, you know, what is it?","index":492,"end_time":1211.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1207.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s a BC place.","index":493,"end_time":1213.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1211.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the seats in BC place if is only like 54,000 people.","index":494,"end_time":1220.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1215.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, right.","index":495,"end_time":1223.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1221.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like a little over 54,000 people.","index":496,"end_time":1225.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1223.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s really not that big.","index":497,"end_time":1227.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1225.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":498,"end_time":1228.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1228.39,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":499,"end_time":1229.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1229.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But to get like, they, like I said, it''s kind of a fuzzy.","index":500,"end_time":1233.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1229.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Not a huge fan of FIFA as the organization.","index":501,"end_time":1236.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1233.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I like watching soccer, but the organization itself, I feel like it''s a bit of a, you know, a bit of a money grab.","index":502,"end_time":1242.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1236.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And so.","index":503,"end_time":1244.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1243.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So they, they opened up like early tickets.","index":504,"end_time":1251.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1246.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But the.","index":505,"end_time":1252.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1251.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But there was nothing open for Vancouver.","index":506,"end_time":1254.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1252.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, I''m not going to like, you know, Houston to watch a game.","index":507,"end_time":1257.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1254.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, that''s not happening.","index":508,"end_time":1258.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1257.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So the only way I could have gotten tickets would have been for like, the premium seats in these, like, fancy sections, which were starting at like, thousands of dollars.","index":509,"end_time":1269.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1258.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then they were like, well, you know, you, you can.","index":510,"end_time":1274.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1270.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Or you can go and put your name in on a list that you pay.","index":511,"end_time":1280.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1274.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think it was like $300 to be put on the list where you might get tickets.","index":512,"end_time":1284.069,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1280.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the 300 is non, non, non refundable.","index":513,"end_time":1287.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1284.069,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, wait, what?","index":514,"end_time":1288.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1287.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, they''re doing that for like, for people in Argentina going crazy because they, they''re like, they''re expecting for Argentina.","index":515,"end_time":1297.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1289.79,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Argentina to play in Miami, where Messi, like, resides right now.","index":516,"end_time":1301.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1297.25,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And it''s like Messi''s last World cup and all the stuff.","index":517,"end_time":1304.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1301.49,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s driving Argentinians crazy.","index":518,"end_time":1305.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1304.13,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"They''re like, asking and requesting for a lot of tickets.","index":519,"end_time":1308.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1305.93,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":520,"end_time":1308.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1308.49,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Myself, I did also like, I requested, but I, I couldn''t get into the.","index":521,"end_time":1312.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1309.01,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":522,"end_time":1313.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1312.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"To the pool of tickets.","index":523,"end_time":1315.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1313.33,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, Messi was supposed to actually come with Miami into Vancouver.","index":524,"end_time":1319.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1315.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I want to say it was last year.","index":525,"end_time":1320.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1319.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because we do have a.","index":526,"end_time":1321.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1320.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We do have a.","index":527,"end_time":1321.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1321.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, we have the Vancouver White House here.","index":528,"end_time":1323.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1321.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":529,"end_time":1324.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1323.69,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And he didn''t get on the plane, didn''t show up.","index":530,"end_time":1328.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1324.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And people spent like, and I''m not joking, thousands of dollars.","index":531,"end_time":1332.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1328.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":532,"end_time":1333.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1332.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There was the biggest like, like stink about it in Vancouver for weeks because they were like, you know, you guys, you know, promoted it that Messi and a bunch of other these really popular players will be coming.","index":533,"end_time":1349.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1333.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Not one of them showed up.","index":534,"end_time":1350.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1349.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I spent, you know, $2,000 a ticket to go to this game.","index":535,"end_time":1354.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1350.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, and people are coming in from out of town, so they''re spending money on hotels and all the rest of it.","index":536,"end_time":1361.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1354.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I was just like, yeah, you know, if it were me, I would be angry too, because that''s what you want to come, you know, you want to see these guys, right?","index":537,"end_time":1369.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1362.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And they don''t show up like, oh, it was so bad.","index":538,"end_time":1371.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1369.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":539,"end_time":1372.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1372.119,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"He did the same thing in Hong Kong.","index":540,"end_time":1375.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1373.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Inter Miami came.","index":541,"end_time":1377.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1375.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":542,"end_time":1377.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1377.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And Hong Kong, like, doesn''t get a lot of professional teams, so, like our biggest stadium fully sold out.","index":543,"end_time":1383.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1377.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The team came.","index":544,"end_time":1384.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1384.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"He like, did the warm up on the pitch and then sat down the entire game.","index":545,"end_time":1389.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1385.02,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Really.","index":546,"end_time":1389.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1389.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"People were so angry.","index":547,"end_time":1391.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1389.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Well, at least he showed up.","index":548,"end_time":1393.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1391.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He didn''t even make it to Vancouver.","index":549,"end_time":1394.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1393.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, there wasn''t.","index":550,"end_time":1395.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1395.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, he didn''t even put get on the plane.","index":551,"end_time":1397.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1396.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And people were just like, oh, they were so, so angry.","index":552,"end_time":1403.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1398.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, yeah, I get it.","index":553,"end_time":1404.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1403.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, you''ve spent literally thousands of dollars because the, the seats were going for, you know, for thousands of dollars apiece.","index":554,"end_time":1412.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1404.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":555,"end_time":1412.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1412.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I just, I''m like, really?","index":556,"end_time":1415.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1412.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, come on.","index":557,"end_time":1416.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1415.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, and it just, it felt like such a cash grab.","index":558,"end_time":1419.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1416.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I felt so, so bad for these people who are like true fans, wanting to see these players and them just not showing up.","index":559,"end_time":1427.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1419.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just disappointing amongst everything else.","index":560,"end_time":1429.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1427.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But, yeah, I mean, there were like huge billboards all over Vancouver, like, come see, you know, like the white caps in Miami and Messi''s gonna be like, literally, his face was plastered all over our city for, for months.","index":561,"end_time":1442.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1431.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":562,"end_time":1443.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1443.33,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I mean, is there any grounds to like, sue for false advertising?","index":563,"end_time":1447.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1443.73,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, there was a bit of that and it quietly went away.","index":564,"end_time":1451.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1448.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I think the, I think people were paid money to keep quiet, but yeah, yeah, yeah, absolutely.","index":565,"end_time":1458.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1451.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So anyway, yeah, FIFA, that''s a whole other situation.","index":566,"end_time":1461.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1458.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''d love to go, but I''m not spending $5,000 a ticket to go or $4,000 a ticket to go crazy.","index":567,"end_time":1469.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1462.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"FIFA is always trying to, like, take the money grabbing into the next level.","index":568,"end_time":1477.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1470.27,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, it always has.","index":569,"end_time":1478.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1477.07,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, it''s so bad.","index":570,"end_time":1479.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1478.35,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It''s so bad.","index":571,"end_time":1481.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1480.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And with this new, like, amount of teams in the World cup, this also, like, searching for, like, more money.","index":572,"end_time":1489.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1482.03,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"More money, more money, more money, more money.","index":573,"end_time":1492.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1489.83,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So it''s like, I''m not, I''m not, like, I''m not surprised.","index":574,"end_time":1498.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1493.37,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, they''re, they''re always, like, doing that.","index":575,"end_time":1501.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1498.05,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"So it''s sad because at the end of the day, there''s people also, like, involved.","index":576,"end_time":1506.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1501.33,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Like, the consumers are the ones that are, will are like, forced to pay more to watch.","index":577,"end_time":1511.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1506.73,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, yeah, absolutely.","index":578,"end_time":1513.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1511.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, there was this NETFLIX documentary because I love a good documentary and I just, I don''t know why I got onto it.","index":579,"end_time":1519.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1513.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just thought oh, this should be interesting, especially with FIFA coming to Vancouver.","index":580,"end_time":1522.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1519.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it''s called FIFA Uncovered.","index":581,"end_time":1524.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1522.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":582,"end_time":1524.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1524.57,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"On Netflix.","index":583,"end_time":1525.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1525.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I watched that, and I was like, oh, my God, these people, like, and it''s all about the money.","index":584,"end_time":1532.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1525.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It has nothing to do with anything else other than how much money they can possibly make.","index":585,"end_time":1536.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1532.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Super corrupt.","index":586,"end_time":1538.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1537.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like.","index":587,"end_time":1538.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1538.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like.","index":588,"end_time":1539.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1538.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, they make politicians look almost good at this point.","index":589,"end_time":1545.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1541.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was like, wow.","index":590,"end_time":1546.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1545.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that''s something.","index":591,"end_time":1547.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1546.87,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":592,"end_time":1551.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1548.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s definitely something.","index":593,"end_time":1552.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1551.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, anyway, well, good luck with the wedding.","index":594,"end_time":1554.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1552.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I hope it all goes well.","index":595,"end_time":1555.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1554.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":596,"end_time":1556.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1555.75,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And like I said, I have absolutely zero sympathy for you for going to a concert the next day.","index":597,"end_time":1561.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1556.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re on your own.","index":598,"end_time":1562.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1561.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I want to, like, disappear from the.","index":599,"end_time":1565.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1564.03,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"From the earth, like, but I paid a lot of money, so I''m like, I''m going.","index":600,"end_time":1572.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1565.67,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I''m going.","index":601,"end_time":1573.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1572.91,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I paid that amount.","index":602,"end_time":1575.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1574.43,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"A lot of money.","index":603,"end_time":1576.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1575.63,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"You''re young.","index":604,"end_time":1577.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1577.32,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"You''ll be fine.","index":605,"end_time":1578.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1577.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Your liver will be fine.","index":606,"end_time":1579.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1578.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Everything will be fine.","index":607,"end_time":1581.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1579.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I. I hope so.","index":608,"end_time":1582.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1581.32,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I hope so.","index":609,"end_time":1583.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1582.84,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Pray for me.","index":610,"end_time":1586.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1586.12,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"That''s the only thing that I''m going to say.","index":611,"end_time":1589.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1587.48,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"What happened to Lou?","index":612,"end_time":1591.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1590.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, he didn''t make it.","index":613,"end_time":1593.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1591.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He didn''t make it.","index":614,"end_time":1594.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1593.8,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"He didn''t make it Fair.","index":615,"end_time":1601.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1594.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I used to do stupid things when I was young, too.","index":616,"end_time":1604.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1601.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, you know, it is what it is.","index":617,"end_time":1605.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1604.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So you''ll be fine.","index":618,"end_time":1607.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1606.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re young.","index":619,"end_time":1607.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1607.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''ll be fine.","index":620,"end_time":1608.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1607.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right, Natalie, what do we got?","index":621,"end_time":1612.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1610.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right, so just wanted to.","index":622,"end_time":1616.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1613.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So quickly for the video, we''re going to have the storyboard ready.","index":623,"end_time":1621.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1616.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Ready for you on Wednesday.","index":624,"end_time":1622.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1621.24,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":625,"end_time":1623.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1622.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s where we''ll outline all of the frames from that video outline that we previously talked about.","index":626,"end_time":1629.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1623.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then I was able to download all of those video files that you added to the folder.","index":627,"end_time":1633.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1629.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":628,"end_time":1634.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1634.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Those are all good to go.","index":629,"end_time":1636.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1634.63,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Excellent.","index":630,"end_time":1637.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1636.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":631,"end_time":1638.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1637.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And where are we at with that brochure, that Optimizer slash template brochure?","index":632,"end_time":1648.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1639.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because I would love to get my hands on some kind of copy of it for a meeting I have on Friday.","index":633,"end_time":1656.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1648.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I have to wrap it up, but I''m going to end.","index":634,"end_time":1659.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1656.99,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I have to wrap it up today, so that''s going.","index":635,"end_time":1661.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1659.67,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":636,"end_time":1662.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1661.47,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":637,"end_time":1662.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1662.57,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":638,"end_time":1663.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1663.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Is there anything you want to walk through, Lou, or.","index":639,"end_time":1666.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1663.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I can show you the icons that the new icon set.","index":640,"end_time":1671.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1668.89,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, please, if you would.","index":641,"end_time":1672.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1671.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":642,"end_time":1673.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1672.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I feel like we''re super close to getting it.","index":643,"end_time":1675.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1673.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think now.","index":644,"end_time":1676.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1675.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think the template, honestly, is good for everything else.","index":645,"end_time":1680.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1676.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think now we''re just fine tuning the content and the look and feel specifically for Optimizer.","index":646,"end_time":1685.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1680.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, look at that.","index":647,"end_time":1688.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1687.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Little power.","index":648,"end_time":1689.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1688.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, that''s nice.","index":649,"end_time":1690.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1689.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This is.","index":650,"end_time":1690.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1690.24,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"This one originally was on the right.","index":651,"end_time":1694.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1690.88,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"The arrow was here.","index":652,"end_time":1695.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1694.32,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"It kind of crashed with the square that we want to introduce, so I switch it out to the other side.","index":653,"end_time":1701.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1696.72,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Okay.","index":654,"end_time":1702.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1702.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And can we do one with the little battery, too?","index":655,"end_time":1704.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1702.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just want to give Linea the two options.","index":656,"end_time":1707.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1704.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Here it is.","index":657,"end_time":1708.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1707.44,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":658,"end_time":1708.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1708.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yay.","index":659,"end_time":1709.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1709.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":660,"end_time":1710.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1710,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Also with this one, we don''t have any solid stuff, so I don''t know if this is going to work.","index":661,"end_time":1717.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1710.72,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I prefer the outline mode, but I don''t know.","index":662,"end_time":1720.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1717.19,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, I could go either way.","index":663,"end_time":1722.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1721.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I see your point.","index":664,"end_time":1723.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1722.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think it''s.","index":665,"end_time":1726.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1725.51,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Somehow the solid gets me there faster because it looks like, you know, it looks like what you see on your phone or whatever.","index":666,"end_time":1734.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1726.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":667,"end_time":1736.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1735.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":668,"end_time":1737.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1736.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, I know aesthetically, you like the outline.","index":669,"end_time":1741.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1737.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Maybe give me two versions.","index":670,"end_time":1743.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1741.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Give me one with the outline, one solid, and then we can see which one Linea likes, and we''ll go from there.","index":671,"end_time":1747.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1743.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s fine.","index":672,"end_time":1748.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1747.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then did the new icons for the optimizer, did that make sense?","index":673,"end_time":1755.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1748.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Did those ones make sense?","index":674,"end_time":1756.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1755.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I.","index":675,"end_time":1759.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1759.12,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Which ones?","index":676,"end_time":1761.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1760.4,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"For the brochure template for the brochure today.","index":677,"end_time":1765.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1762,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Ah.","index":678,"end_time":1766.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1766.01,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I. I didn''t get to, like, see that in a good.","index":679,"end_time":1769.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1766.41,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Let me check, because I read through all the.","index":680,"end_time":1773.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1770.41,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, let me open my note.","index":681,"end_time":1776.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1774.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There is a bit.","index":682,"end_time":1777.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1776.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was a bit.","index":683,"end_time":1778.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1777.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, here it is.","index":684,"end_time":1779.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1778.29,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Reduce labor costs.","index":685,"end_time":1780.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1779.53,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, yeah, absolutely.","index":686,"end_time":1784.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1783.37,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yes.","index":687,"end_time":1785.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1784.81,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Okay.","index":688,"end_time":1786.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1785.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes.","index":689,"end_time":1786.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1786.49,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Because there''s a lot of.","index":690,"end_time":1787.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1786.89,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"From these icons that you want to introduce.","index":691,"end_time":1790.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1787.89,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"There''s a lot of, like, reusable assets from the different icons that we can use.","index":692,"end_time":1793.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1790.05,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":693,"end_time":1794.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1793.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I didn''t want you to reinvent the wheel.","index":694,"end_time":1796.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1794.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, we have the elements all ready to go, and I just need, like, you know, for.","index":695,"end_time":1800.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1796.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think it was, like, reduced costs.","index":696,"end_time":1802.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1800.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just need the arrow to go.","index":697,"end_time":1803.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1802.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, I just need the thing to go down.","index":698,"end_time":1805.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1803.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":699,"end_time":1806.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1805.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it was just sort of like mirroring it and flipping it, Stuff like that.","index":700,"end_time":1810.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1806.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that would be.","index":701,"end_time":1812.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1811.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that would be good.","index":702,"end_time":1813.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1812.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What else did I have on there?","index":703,"end_time":1816.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1814.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think the rest of it was pretty straightforward.","index":704,"end_time":1818.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1816.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let me see.","index":705,"end_time":1825.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1824.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":706,"end_time":1828.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1828.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So, yeah, it was to make the balloons that, like, arc radiation on it.","index":707,"end_time":1837.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1832.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":708,"end_time":1838.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1837.97,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I. I adjusted the hero image in a very specific way.","index":709,"end_time":1841.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1838.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So please don''t move it.","index":710,"end_time":1842.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1841.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Add in the.","index":711,"end_time":1845.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1843.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What was it over.","index":712,"end_time":1849.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1848.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, for the template, the gray was looking a little like the gray tab, if you will, along the bottom of it was looking a little bit washed out.","index":713,"end_time":1858.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1849.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So Linea wanted to just get rid of it, which was fine.","index":714,"end_time":1862.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1859.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I. I don''t.","index":715,"end_time":1863.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1862.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t hate it.","index":716,"end_time":1863.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1863.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It actually gives the page A little bit more space and a little bit more flexibility.","index":717,"end_time":1867.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1863.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I think that was fine.","index":718,"end_time":1869.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1867.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"See, what else did I have on there?","index":719,"end_time":1874.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1872.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was.","index":720,"end_time":1875.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1874.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just did the green print images, so they kind of spanned over that white tab and into.","index":721,"end_time":1882.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1877,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Towards the, you know, towards the middle of the page.","index":722,"end_time":1885,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1882.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We like that layering, so that was good.","index":723,"end_time":1888.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1885.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Added back in the gift card and hopefully.","index":724,"end_time":1893.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1890.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Natalie, were you able to pull down those files from the.","index":725,"end_time":1897.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1894.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I got the Illustrator files and then the images.","index":726,"end_time":1902.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1898.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":727,"end_time":1903.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1903.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":728,"end_time":1904.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1903.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right.","index":729,"end_time":1905.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1904.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that was my bad.","index":730,"end_time":1906.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1905.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I thought it was all in that links file, but it wasn''t.","index":731,"end_time":1909.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1906.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I pulled down all the images.","index":732,"end_time":1911.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1909.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I gave you more than you needed, but I''m like, here, take them all.","index":733,"end_time":1915.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1912.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that if something doesn''t work, maybe we can use, you know, we can always use something else.","index":734,"end_time":1919.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1915.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That was totally fine.","index":735,"end_time":1920.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1919.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then those three icons, so the reduced labor icon and then an optimized materials icon, and then the enhanced efficiency icon, which I gave you guys some samples.","index":736,"end_time":1933.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1920.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then the Optimizer image on page three, we updated with like, more of the GUI as opposed to one of the reports.","index":737,"end_time":1943.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1935.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then I changed some.","index":738,"end_time":1946.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1944.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We changed some of the content.","index":739,"end_time":1947.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1946.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''m like, please don''t change any content.","index":740,"end_time":1949.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1947.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I think that was it.","index":741,"end_time":1951.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1951.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There was just some stuff I wanted to point out that just like, please don''t change it.","index":742,"end_time":1955.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1951.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then there were other things that needed to be actually done, like the balloons and the icons and stuff like that.","index":743,"end_time":1961.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1955.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":744,"end_time":1961.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1961.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah, if I could get a copy of that of, like, whatever it looks like, you know, tomorrow morning.","index":745,"end_time":1968.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1963.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let''s see.","index":746,"end_time":1969.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1969.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"My meeting is with.","index":747,"end_time":1971.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1970.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Is tomorrow at 10 o'' clock my time, so if I can get it before that, I would be over the moon.","index":748,"end_time":1979.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1972.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, sure.","index":749,"end_time":1981.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1980.79,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":750,"end_time":1982.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1981.67,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":751,"end_time":1982.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1982.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s going to be on today, so I will send it to Natalie today.","index":752,"end_time":1985.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1982.87,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"All right, super.","index":753,"end_time":1986.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1985.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"A couple of hours, I think we''ll have it done, so.","index":754,"end_time":1989.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1986.92,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, super.","index":755,"end_time":1990.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1989.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":756,"end_time":1990.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1990.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m just.","index":757,"end_time":1991.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1990.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m meeting with the product manager, and if I can just, you know, I''ll run through it with her and get her to sign it off, that means I can move it into my final review process.","index":758,"end_time":2000.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1991.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that''s what I''m desperately trying to do.","index":759,"end_time":2002.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2000.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Optimizer will be launching January 10th, and I know that feels like it''s a long way off, but I have to get things done 30 days ahead of time.","index":760,"end_time":2012.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2003.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s December 10th and we are in November.","index":761,"end_time":2015.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2013.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So this is my.","index":762,"end_time":2017.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2016.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"My push to get everything done in, you know, in enough time.","index":763,"end_time":2021.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2017.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":764,"end_time":2022.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2021.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":765,"end_time":2023.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2022.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":766,"end_time":2023.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2023.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right.","index":767,"end_time":2024.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2024.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And what else did you have.","index":768,"end_time":2025.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2024.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Natalie, I think you had one other thing on your list.","index":769,"end_time":2027.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2025.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, that''s it.","index":770,"end_time":2029,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2028.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I had the brochure, the icons, and then the animated video.","index":771,"end_time":2032.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2029.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, all right, very good.","index":772,"end_time":2035.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2033.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":773,"end_time":2036.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2036.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So as we settle on this template, I''ll and get.","index":774,"end_time":2042.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2037,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m getting content sort of ready to go for both Info Print Manager and for RICO Process Director.","index":775,"end_time":2050.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2042.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Once I have the PMs happy with how those look, I''ll be sending them over to you guys to clean up for me and you know, put into place and whatnot.","index":776,"end_time":2058.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2050.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I have been just very roughly putting content down because it is helpful to see, see like how much content and how it fits on the page and whether or not we need to, you know, go down in some content or whatnot.","index":777,"end_time":2072.429,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2059.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So because the, the template is a little bit different space wise.","index":778,"end_time":2076.189,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2072.429,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''ve been doing that just to give people a look and feel and it''s also good for the PMs to understand what it''s going to look like as well, so especially with a refresh.","index":779,"end_time":2084.189,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2076.189,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So anyways, you''ll be getting files from me on those, hopefully sooner rather than later.","index":780,"end_time":2089.309,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2084.349,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":781,"end_time":2090.589,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2090.029,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":782,"end_time":2092.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2092,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Otherwise I think we''re in a good place.","index":783,"end_time":2095.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2092.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Unless you guys have anything else.","index":784,"end_time":2097.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2095.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, no, that''s it.","index":785,"end_time":2099.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2098.32,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":786,"end_time":2101.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2100.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right, well, very good.","index":787,"end_time":2102.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2101.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ll keep my eyes peeled then for everything.","index":788,"end_time":2104.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2102.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And yeah, if there''s anything else, of course.","index":789,"end_time":2108.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2106,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"In the meantime, please let me know.","index":790,"end_time":2109.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2108.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Otherwise, I hope you guys have a good rest of your day.","index":791,"end_time":2112.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2109.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":792,"end_time":2115.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2114.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":793,"end_time":2115.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2115.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Take care soon.","index":794,"end_time":2117.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2116,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Bye.","index":795,"end_time":2118,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2117.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Bye.","index":796,"end_time":2118.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2118,"speaker_name":"Roz"}],"dateString":"2025-11-06T17:30:00.000Z","host_email":"nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85828735088?pwd=b9W3cDKwBeJQyK00Qs0iP3vvCmTxIZ.1","participants":["nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,lou.bogani@marketersindemand.com,kiyan.klocker@marketersindemand.com,rosalynne.regan@ricoh.ca,linnea.wolken@ricoh-usa.com","colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","lou.bogani@marketersindemand.com","kiyan.klocker@marketersindemand.com","rosalynne.regan@ricoh.ca","linnea.wolken@ricoh-usa.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01K98504YTQ8HZDTH79AE00PER","organizer_email":"nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.87,"bullets":["Confirmed storyboard for animated video will be delivered Wednesday, covering all outlined frames.","Lou committed to finishing Optimizer brochure today for Roz''s Friday meeting with product manager.","Roz requested two icon versions—outline and solid—so Linea can choose preferred visual style.","Final Optimizer brochure assets to include updated GUI images, refined icons, and layered artwork.","Launch for Optimizer set for January 10; Roz aims to finalize assets by December 10 deadline."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Optimizer will be launching January 10th... I have to get things done 30 days ahead of time.","speaker":"Roz"},{"quote":"I have to wrap it up today... I will send it to Natalie today.","speaker":"Lou Bogani"},{"quote":"I feel like we''re super close... now we''re just fine tuning the content and the look and feel.","speaker":"Roz"}],"topics":["delivery","launch","design","video"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-11-13T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Wedding Costs and Planning Insights**\n\nThe discussion highlighted the steep costs and complexity involved in wedding planning, underscoring the need to balance budget and experience effectively.\n\n- **Roz** shared that her wedding for **about 50 people cost around $15,000** (08:57), with venue, food, and decor being major expenses.\n    - She secured a private club venue for **$500 in August and September**, which included tables, chairs, linens, plates, and cutlery (04:20).\n    - The event manager’s exceptional service was critical to a smooth experience, earning a generous tip for her role (11:00).\n    - Unforeseen personal issues arose, such as a family member''s injury and last-minute Covid infections, impacting attendance (06:30).\n    - Roz emphasized the hidden workload in wedding logistics even when the venue is fully equipped (11:28).\n\n- **Lou Bogani** described his brother’s upcoming wedding in **Buenos Aires with 180 guests and a budget over $40,000** (09:16).\n    - The event will feature a relaxed style with food islands and a late-night party, reflecting a more informal reception approach (10:00).\n    - Lou recognized the value of the special moment but questioned the cost-to-duration ratio of weddings (11:54).\n    - He is personally juggling significant wedding prep stress while also planning to attend a major concert the day after (14:00).\n\n- Both Roz and Lou agreed smaller, more intimate weddings or eloping followed by a party could be cost-effective alternatives without losing the celebration’s spirit (12:16).\n    - Roz’s husband preferred a traditional ceremony with details like cake cutting and first dance, illustrating varying expectations that impact planning (13:18).\n\n## **Event Scheduling and Personal Impact**\n\nThe timing of Lou’s brother’s wedding and the adjacent major concert created logistical and personal challenges, affecting resource and energy planning.\n\n- The wedding is scheduled for **Saturday, November 15th**, followed by attending an **Oasis concert at River Plate Stadium with 100,000 attendees** the next day (14:15).\n    - Lou expects the wedding to end around **6 AM**, leaving limited recovery time before heading to the stadium at **4 PM** for the concert starting at **9 PM** (15:56).\n    - He anticipates arriving home around **2 AM the following morning**, risking exhaustion and vocal strain (17:38).\n    - Lou plans to request a **day off on Monday for recovery**, acknowledging the physical toll of back-to-back events (15:46).\n\n- The concert is a major event as part of Oasis’s world tour after a **16-year hiatus since 2009**, with two sold-out shows totaling **approximately 200,000 attendees** (18:30).\n    - The scale and timing of the wedding and concert combination reflect complex personal scheduling challenges for Lou and his family (16:52).\n\n## **Venue and Service Provider Selection**\n\nChoosing the right venue and service providers proved crucial to managing costs and ensuring a quality experience.\n\n- Roz praised the private club’s all-inclusive setup, which reduced vendor coordination by providing furniture, tableware, and kitchen facilities, saving time and complexity (04:20).\n    - The event manager’s hands-on role ensured smooth operations, reducing stress and allowing the couple to focus on the celebration (11:00).\n    - The florist delivered a large quantity of high-quality flowers for **$1,800**, which Roz felt was underpriced given the quality (05:30).\n\n- Lou described his brother’s wedding at a golf club venue with an outdoor tent, emphasizing a relaxed but well-styled atmosphere that fits their budget and guest experience goals (09:30).\n\n## **Product Brochure and Marketing Collateral Progress**\n\nThe team is advancing the Optimizer brochure and related assets with a focus on finalizing content and visuals ahead of critical deadlines.\n\n- **Lou Bogani** committed to completing the Optimizer brochure template today, aiming to deliver it to **Natalie Mintjens by Wednesday** for storyboard review (27:02, 33:02).\n    - He presented new icon options including outlined and solid versions to provide design flexibility for client feedback (28:00).\n    - Roz emphasized the need for content fine-tuning specifically tailored for Optimizer, with a goal to finalize by **December 10th** for the January 10th launch (33:09).\n    - The team is reusing existing icon assets where possible to speed up delivery and maintain consistency (29:40).\n    - Roz asked to retain specific hero image adjustments and content positioning to preserve the intended look and feel (30:35).\n\n- Natalie confirmed receipt of all necessary video and graphic files, enabling ongoing progress on animation and brochure development (27:14, 31:38).\n    - Roz plans to prepare similar collateral for Info Print Manager and RICO Process Director, aiming for early review cycles with product managers (33:53).\n\n## **Market and Event Ticketing Context**\n\nThe conversation revealed frustration around sports event ticket availability and pricing, highlighting challenges in large-scale event accessibility.\n\n- Roz described the **FIFA World Cup ticket situation in Vancouver**, where the largest stadium holds just over **54,000 seats** and premium tickets sell for thousands of dollars, limiting access (19:51).\n    - She criticized FIFA’s pricing and early ticketing practices as a cash grab, echoing dissatisfaction with similar issues in other markets (20:30).\n    - Lou noted that high demand is driven by star players like **Messi**, especially as this might be his last World Cup, increasing pressure on ticket sales in Miami and Argentina (21:00).\n    - Roz explained a recent incident where Messi did not attend a promoted event in Vancouver, causing public outrage and accusations of false advertising (22:30).\n    - Both Roz and Nathalie shared examples of fan disappointment and frustration in Hong Kong and Vancouver due to incomplete player appearances at matches (23:00).\n\n- The team watched the Netflix documentary **FIFA Uncovered**, confirming widespread corruption and financial motives behind FIFA’s operations, which further erodes fan trust (25:20).\n\n## **Team Coordination and Deadlines**\n\nClear deadlines and collaborative coordination are driving the final stages of the Optimizer launch preparations.\n\n- Roz’s meeting with the product manager is set for **Wednesday at 10 AM**, requiring an updated brochure draft beforehand to secure approval (33:00).\n    - Lou is prioritizing final icon adjustments, balloon design arcs, and hero image fixes to meet this deadline (30:28).\n    - Roz is actively preparing content for additional product brochures, signaling a broader refresh initiative within marketing collateral (33:50).\n    - Natalie is tasked with integrating all assets and ensuring files are ready for animation and final edits (31:38).\n    - The launch timeline demands all materials be finalized by **December 10th**, supporting the **January 10th Optimizer product launch** (33:09).","outline":null,"keywords":["wedding planning","event management","Optimizer brochure","world cup tickets","Oasis concert","FIFA corruption"],"overview":"- **Wedding Costs:** Roz’s wedding for 50 guests cost $15,000; venue, food, and decor were major expenses.  \n- **Brother''s Wedding:** Lou''s brother’s wedding in Buenos Aires will host 180 guests with a budget over $40,000.  \n- **Event Scheduling:** Lou faces challenges planning his brother''s wedding on November 15th, followed by an Oasis concert the next day.  \n- **Venue Selection:** All-inclusive venues simplify logistics; Roz praised her private club for reducing vendor coordination.  \n- **Ticketing Challenges:** FIFA World Cup tickets in Vancouver are expensive and limited; demand rises with star players like Messi.  \n- **Project Deadlines:** The Optimizer launch requires all materials finalized by December 10th for a January 10th release.","action_items":"\n**Lou Bogani**\nFinalize and deliver the Optimizer/template brochure by end of day (27:36)\nProvide both outline and solid versions of new icons for selection by Linea (27:43)\n\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nPrepare storyboard for the upcoming video by Wednesday (27:02)\n\n**Roz Regan**\nSubmit rough content drafts of brochures for Info Print Manager and RICO Process Director to team for further refinement (34:58)\nShare finalized brochure copy with product manager by Friday meeting for sign-off (27:36)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"3579070f-bf40-421a-ab62-3814d3b5c022","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
