    '{"id":"01K9QBWARH87KQ8QGDMCSXHAD5","title":"New North x Sedra Solutions: Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Video Project and Content Updates**\n\nThe video projects are nearly finalized with precise caption corrections and content alignment improving clarity and consistency.\n\n- **Final caption edit identified for the Ponzi term in Arabic, correcting mismatched spellings to ensure accuracy** (01:08)  \n    - Fahad pointed out the inconsistency between two Arabic captions needing alignment.  \n    - Taylor confirmed the fix and planned to update immediately for quality assurance.  \n    - Ensuring correct translation is critical to avoid confusion and maintain credibility in target markets.  \n    - This final step will help close out a complicated video project phase with confidence.\n\n- **Procurement video updates now include new screenshots integrated into multiple scenes for clarity and consistency** (02:02)  \n    - Jackie approved the updated visuals after confirming numbers matched source data.  \n    - Taylor will advance animation work following final approval to meet project timelines.  \n    - These visuals aim to improve viewer comprehension and align messaging across channels.  \n    - The updated video supports broader content strategy by enhancing organic social posts planned for release this week.\n\n- **Organic Social content streamlining underway, with Fahad tasked to develop new post formats and ideas** (02:54)  \n    - Taylor will submit new posts for Jackie’s review and approval before scheduling in Publer.  \n    - Fahad is expected to deliver fresh concepts aligned with ongoing engagement goals by month-end.  \n    - This phased content refresh responds to audience feedback and aims to maintain consistent brand presence.  \n    - The flexible timeline reduces immediate pressure but encourages steady momentum.\n\n## **Outreach and ABM Campaign Strategy**\n\nThe outreach messaging and demo efforts are facing challenges prompting a shift toward more direct, problem-focused communications to boost engagement.\n\n- **Demo scheduling efforts hit a setback with a last-minute cancellation, highlighting rescheduling difficulties** (03:37)  \n    - Fahad reported a demo cancellation due to client conflicts and ongoing attempts to reschedule.  \n    - Taylor emphasized the importance of follow-up and patience in securing demo opportunities.  \n    - This reflects common hurdles in B2B sales cycles requiring persistent contact strategies.  \n    - The team remains committed to tracking and supporting demo reschedules to convert leads.\n\n- **LinkedIn outreach sequence simplified to a single message to increase clarity and reduce contact fatigue** (04:09)  \n    - Taylor confirmed changes to LinkedIn messaging to focus on direct calls to action for demos.  \n    - Email sequences under review, with proposals to reduce message count and prioritize demo booking links.  \n    - Jackie advocated for straightforward, easy-to-act-upon emails over open-ended questions to prompt responses.  \n    - The planned restructuring targets faster engagement and clearer value propositions.\n\n- **Fahad and Jackie agree outreach emails need to be more personal, direct, and focused on solving client pain points** (09:21)  \n    - Fahad noted current messages lack urgency and clear problem-solution framing, limiting response rates.  \n    - Jackie suggested incorporating ISO certification and security assurances upfront to add credibility and attract interest.  \n    - Taylor will revise emails to sound less robotic and more conversational to better connect with prospects.  \n    - This approach reflects a strategic shift to improve perceived relevance and trustworthiness.\n\n- **Data-driven messaging enhancements proposed using concrete metrics like “90% reduction in data ingestion time”** (12:08)  \n    - Fahad recommended highlighting quantifiable benefits to capture attention and validate claims.  \n    - Jackie volunteered to refine email copy using existing performance data for sharper impact.  \n    - Taylor committed to sending current drafts for iteration and alignment with Fahad’s input.  \n    - The goal is to create punchy, benefit-led emails that quickly convey key advantages.\n\n- **A positive lead emerged from word-of-mouth referral by Mince Group, leading to a scheduled demo with a large law firm** (14:18)  \n    - Fahad shared a demo booked with Boyce Schiller, facilitated by a trusted partner’s recommendation.  \n    - This validates the long-term brand-building efforts through marketing and relationship cultivation.  \n    - Taylor and Jackie recognized this as evidence of steady progress despite slow initial response.  \n    - The team sees referrals as critical for accelerating pipeline development alongside paid campaigns.\n\n## **Paid Media and Advertising Budget Optimization**\n\nReallocating ad spend from underperforming Google Ads to LinkedIn campaigns aims to improve lead quality and cost efficiency.\n\n- **Google Ads underperform on lead generation, prompting recommendation to pause and redirect budget to LinkedIn** (16:34)  \n    - Taylor’s analysis showed limited returns from Google Ads except for broad keywords like “forensic accounting software.”  \n    - Paid media specialist advised reallocating the **$1,500** monthly Google budget into LinkedIn for better targeting and engagement.  \n    - The new LinkedIn campaign will focus on website conversions driving prospects to the demo landing page.  \n    - Future retargeting Google campaigns may resume once LinkedIn data identifies higher-quality leads.\n\n- **LinkedIn ads currently generate about nine leads per month with strong engagement from key decision-makers** (17:44)  \n    - Taylor noted LinkedIn delivers top-of-funnel leads by exchanging downloadable guides for contact info.  \n    - Ad budget totals planned at **$3,000** monthly all allocated to LinkedIn for improved ROI.  \n    - Impressions and clicks mostly come from partners, associates, and founders in major metro areas, showing good audience fit.  \n    - Weekly monitoring and budget shifts toward best-performing ads will maintain campaign effectiveness.\n\n- **ABM ads maintain steady performance with 14 clicks on AdRoll and 19 clicks on LinkedIn in November** (20:14)  \n    - Cost per click decreased, improving overall campaign efficiency and cost management.  \n    - Top-performing ads highlight financial investigative solutions and case studies, reflecting resonance with target segments.  \n    - Continuous weekly budget adjustments optimize spend toward highest-impact ads.  \n    - This sustained activity supports pipeline building despite broader budget reallocations.\n\n- **Team consensus supports shifting ad budget to LinkedIn for direct demo conversion while keeping SEO focus on ‘Cedra’ keyword** (19:39)  \n    - Jackie confirmed priority on ranking number one for Cedra remains unchanged despite pausing some Google Ads.  \n    - Taylor reassured that core keyword targeting will continue alongside the new campaign approach.  \n    - This balanced strategy preserves brand visibility while maximizing immediate lead generation impact.  \n    - Weekly reporting will ensure transparency and agility in budget and campaign adjustments.\n\n## **Long-Term Marketing and Brand Positioning**\n\nThe team recognizes marketing as a gradual process relying on sustained exposure and referral networks for eventual success.\n\n- **Brand recognition efforts through repeated marketing touches are creating awareness leading to referrals and demo opportunities** (15:27)  \n    - Jackie illustrated how multiple exposures over months led prospects to recall and engage with the brand.  \n    - Fahad highlighted the importance of trusted introductions from partners like Mince Group in accelerating trust.  \n    - Word-of-mouth remains a powerful driver of qualified leads beyond paid campaigns.  \n    - The team views current marketing as foundational groundwork for future growth.\n\n- **Messaging will evolve to emphasize real client problems and clear solutions, reflecting a shift from general marketing to consultative selling** (10:30)  \n    - Fahad stressed the need to focus on reducing investigation time and simplifying workflows as key selling points.  \n    - Taylor and Jackie agreed messaging must quickly show how the product solves urgent client pains.  \n    - This approach aligns with feedback that generic marketing language lacks impact with sophisticated audiences.  \n    - The shift aims to improve demo conversion rates and overall campaign effectiveness.\n\n- **Ongoing collaboration between marketing and sales teams is critical to refine messaging, targeting, and outreach tactics** (14:05)  \n    - Taylor emphasized incorporating Fahad’s frontline insights to tailor outreach for better resonance.  \n    - Jackie committed to ideating sharper email copy using performance data and client feedback.  \n    - Fahad’s upcoming submission of competitor campaign examples will inform adjustments.  \n    - This cross-team alignment ensures continuous improvement and strategic coherence.","outline":null,"keywords":["Video Captions","Outreach Email Sequence","Paid Media Budget","LinkedIn Campaigns","ABM Demo Lead","Messaging Strategy"],"overview":"- **Video project updates:** Final caption edits for Arabic ensure accuracy and completion of complex video projects. \n\n- **Outreach messaging adjustment:** Simplified LinkedIn outreach aims for direct communication and reduced fatigue to boost engagement rates.\n\n- **Ad budget reallocation:** Shift from Google Ads to LinkedIn campaigns to improve lead quality, with $1,500 redirected monthly.\n\n- **Lead generation success:** Nine leads per month from LinkedIn, focusing on high-level decision-makers and targeted campaign strategies.\n\n- **Brand awareness growth:** Ongoing marketing efforts and trusted referrals significantly enhance brand recognition and demo opportunities.\n\n- **Collaborative focus:** Sales and marketing teams align on messaging to enhance client engagement and direct outreach effectiveness.","action_items":"\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nUpdate final Arabic caption spelling to correct discrepancies in video project (01:52)\nSend procurement video screenshot update for Jackie’s review post-meeting (02:42)\nPrepare and send new Organic Social posts for review this week (02:54)\nRestructure email outreach sequence focused on direct demo booking CTAs; send updated draft to Fahad and Jackie for input (07:20)\nSend current outreach email sequence link to Jackie for ideation (13:55)\nCreate new LinkedIn paid media campaign reallocating $1500 from Google Ads budget to focus on demo landing page conversion (16:55)\nContinue monitoring paid media performance and report stats weekly to clients (20:55)\n\n**Jackie Wheeler**\nReview procurement video updates and confirm accuracy of numbers/screenshots (02:41)\nProvide input and ideate on shorter, more direct outreach email content incorporating impactful statistics and ISO certification (13:53)\n\n**Fahad Almutawa**\nProvide feedback on outreach messaging to ensure problem-solution orientation and relevance to target ICP (12:00)\nShare example of demo outreach email that generated a response from 1 in 400 to help improve messaging practices (10:15)\nContinue efforts to reschedule cancelled ABM demo and update team accordingly (03:50)\n"},"duration":21.959999084472656,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"id":1,"name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"id":2,"name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"id":3,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"}],"sentences":[{"text":"It''s a.","index":0,"end_time":0.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s a big change up.","index":1,"end_time":2.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s a huge change, but I love it.","index":2,"end_time":4.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2.4,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":3,"end_time":5.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":4.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":4,"end_time":5.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":5.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I.","index":5,"end_time":6.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":5.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s gonna get lighter because my hair was blonde.","index":6,"end_time":8.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":6.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It took the color, like, deep, so I was like, whoa.","index":7,"end_time":11.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":8.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Alarmed.","index":8,"end_time":12.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":11.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I guess a couple washes will make it more of, like, a.","index":9,"end_time":15.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"A light brown.","index":10,"end_time":16.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":15.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I keep catching myself in the mirror, and I''m having, like, imposter syndrome.","index":11,"end_time":20.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":16.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Who is that?","index":12,"end_time":21.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":20.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So once came out of a salon.","index":13,"end_time":23.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":21.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And my hair was black.","index":14,"end_time":24.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":23.88,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I was like, when have you done.","index":15,"end_time":27.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":25.2,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I know.","index":16,"end_time":28.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":27.98,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yes.","index":17,"end_time":29.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":29.02,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It faded.","index":18,"end_time":30.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":29.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":19,"end_time":30.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":30.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I want to do something, like, darker for fall.","index":20,"end_time":32.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":30.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But, yeah, this is.","index":21,"end_time":33.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":32.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hopefully it''ll get a little lighter in the color.","index":22,"end_time":35.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":33.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I love it.","index":23,"end_time":36.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":35.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s great.","index":24,"end_time":36.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":36.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":25,"end_time":37.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":36.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Appreciate it.","index":26,"end_time":39.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":38.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hi, Fahad.","index":27,"end_time":40.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":39.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"How are you?","index":28,"end_time":40.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":40.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hi.","index":29,"end_time":41.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":41.02,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"How are you guys?","index":30,"end_time":42.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":41.42,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Good.","index":31,"end_time":42.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":42.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good.","index":32,"end_time":43.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":42.779,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All right, let me pull this up.","index":33,"end_time":46.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":44.14,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All right.","index":34,"end_time":52.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":51.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So just to start off for the video projects, I just wanted to confirm with you, Fahad.","index":35,"end_time":57.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know Anas just left this one additional caption edit.","index":36,"end_time":61.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Was there anything else that you guys noticed or is this probably the final edit?","index":37,"end_time":65.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know this has been a tricky one, so just want to see.","index":38,"end_time":68.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":65.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, Just with my last.","index":39,"end_time":70.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":68.77,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"When I looked at it was where it says Ponzi in Arabic.","index":40,"end_time":75.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":71.49,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"The one up top says it completely different than the one below.","index":41,"end_time":78.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":75.25,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Okay.","index":42,"end_time":79.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":78.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Which you wouldn''t.","index":43,"end_time":81.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":80.69,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"You know, you can''t read this.","index":44,"end_time":82.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":81.61,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But that was the final edit, hopefully.","index":45,"end_time":85.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":82.65,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Okay, so when she says the caption is misspelled here, is she meaning this or are you saying that there''s some.","index":46,"end_time":92.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":86.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No, you see the one that''s highlighted?","index":47,"end_time":95.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":92.65,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"That''s fine.","index":48,"end_time":96.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":95.73,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"The one next to it.","index":49,"end_time":97.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":96.25,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"This one should be spelling like the one on top.","index":50,"end_time":102.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":99.05,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"The last bullet point, the last word.","index":51,"end_time":104.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":102.49,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"This one here?","index":52,"end_time":106.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":105.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":53,"end_time":106.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":106.49,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"This looks completely different than the one below, as you can see.","index":54,"end_time":109.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":106.97,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":55,"end_time":110.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":109.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":56,"end_time":110.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":110.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m glad I asked.","index":57,"end_time":111.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":110.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":58,"end_time":113.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":112.86,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, we can update that.","index":59,"end_time":114.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":113.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":60,"end_time":115.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":114.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yep.","index":61,"end_time":115.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":115.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I just wanted to walk through it sometimes easier on video.","index":62,"end_time":117.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":115.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know this one''s been tricky, so perfect.","index":63,"end_time":120.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":117.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We will make that adjustment.","index":64,"end_time":122.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":120.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I still find it tricky myself, so.","index":65,"end_time":124.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":122.62,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I don''t believe you.","index":66,"end_time":124.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":124.3,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Oh, really?","index":67,"end_time":125.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":124.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":68,"end_time":126.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":125.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":69,"end_time":127.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":127.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Want to make sure we get the translation right.","index":70,"end_time":130.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":128.14,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then for the procurement video, Jackie, I want to show these updates.","index":71,"end_time":134.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":130.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know Bailey discussed with you these changes last week, so we went ahead and reflected what is on the screenshot into.","index":72,"end_time":141.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":134.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Can make it bigger here into these vid things, little squares.","index":73,"end_time":147.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":141.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we have that.","index":74,"end_time":147.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":147.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then we''re also.","index":75,"end_time":148.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":147.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They''re in the middle of these edits.","index":76,"end_time":149.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":148.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I wanted to share with you when I got the first one back, we''re going to add this screenshot to these additional scenes here.","index":77,"end_time":155.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":149.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But does this look good up here?","index":78,"end_time":157.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":155.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because once we just add those screenshots, we''ll go ahead and start animating.","index":79,"end_time":160.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":157.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":80,"end_time":161.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":161.04,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Assuming the numbers are correct.","index":81,"end_time":162.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":161.4,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yes, that''s correct.","index":82,"end_time":163.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":162.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":83,"end_time":164.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":164.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":84,"end_time":165.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":164.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think go ahead and send it to two after the meeting if you want to take a closer look.","index":85,"end_time":168.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":165.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we just put what was reflected in the screenshot and into the.","index":86,"end_time":171.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":168.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Those squares.","index":87,"end_time":172.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":171.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":88,"end_time":173.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":172.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Now it tells a consistent story.","index":89,"end_time":174.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":173.01,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So that''s great.","index":90,"end_time":175.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":174.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely perfect.","index":91,"end_time":177.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":175.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we will go ahead and get that animation going for Organic Social.","index":92,"end_time":182.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":177.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll be sending some new posts this week for the main page for your review and then once we have your approvals on those, we can get those scheduled into Publer.","index":93,"end_time":189.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":182.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know Fahad, you''re going to be working on kind of giving us a format like this again with some ideas.","index":94,"end_time":195.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":189.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So whenever we have those, we can just pull those together.","index":95,"end_time":198.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":195.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think you have posts still running through the end of the month, so not as much of a time crunch on those.","index":96,"end_time":203.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":198.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But whenever you have time, love to get your insights.","index":97,"end_time":206.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":203.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Sure.","index":98,"end_time":207.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":207.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then ABM campaign.","index":99,"end_time":211.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":209.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m really curious to hear how your demo went.","index":100,"end_time":214.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":211.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Was excited to see that lead come in.","index":101,"end_time":216.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":214.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"How did that conversation go?","index":102,"end_time":217.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":216.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They canceled it though.","index":103,"end_time":219.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":217.68,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":104,"end_time":220.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":220.4,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":105,"end_time":221.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":220.88,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Got cancelled the day before or that same morning.","index":106,"end_time":225,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":221.32,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"The conflicting meeting.","index":107,"end_time":226.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":225,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"They had a client meeting.","index":108,"end_time":227.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":226.2,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Been trying to reschedule ever since.","index":109,"end_time":229.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":227.8,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"We tried to reach out again today.","index":110,"end_time":231.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":229.96,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"He''s traveling.","index":111,"end_time":232.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":231.64,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"We got that email response of travel.","index":112,"end_time":235.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":232.36,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":113,"end_time":236,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it didn''t happen yet.","index":114,"end_time":236.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":236,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I would have updated you so there was nothing to share there yet.","index":115,"end_time":239.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":236.92,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Bummer.","index":116,"end_time":240.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":239.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, I hope that you''re able to reschedule.","index":117,"end_time":242.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":240.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s.","index":118,"end_time":243.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":242.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s such a bummer.","index":119,"end_time":244.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":243.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hate when that happens.","index":120,"end_time":245.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":244.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Then you got to track him down again.","index":121,"end_time":247,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":245.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":122,"end_time":248.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":247.64,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But we''ll.","index":123,"end_time":249.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":249,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ll wait to hear back from you and see if you''re able to get that down.","index":124,"end_time":252.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":249.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As far as the outreach sequence, we did update the LinkedIn sequence according to.","index":125,"end_time":258.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":254.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know Bailey talked about this last week with you guys to just have that one message now so we don''t have several messages going out.","index":126,"end_time":265.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":258.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I wanted to double check before we make any changes to the email sequence.","index":127,"end_time":269.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":265.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We have that current one running now with the different offers that we have.","index":128,"end_time":274.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":269.719,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know we''ve talked about kind of slimming this down and making it more straight to the point for a demo.","index":129,"end_time":279,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":274.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I had sent this sequence back a couple weeks ago where we made the changes to the messages for LinkedIn, but I had sent this idea over for the two emails where we would just be talking about having that demo scheduled instead.","index":130,"end_time":295.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":279.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can just go ahead and add the link in for Fahad''s availability to make it easier without the back and forth.","index":131,"end_time":302.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":296.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I want to confirm that this is what you''re thinking for the LinkedIn sequence right now before we have an exact offer.","index":132,"end_time":308.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":302.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Having only two emails will help us kind of get through those contacts a little bit quicker too.","index":133,"end_time":313.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":309.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know we have a lot of different campaign segments, so is this kind of what you''re thinking as far as email change to the sequence where it''s just you talk about kind of like what you do in the LinkedIn messaging, a little bit about, etc.","index":134,"end_time":329.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":313.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But then you ask like, would it be worth a 15 minute chat?","index":135,"end_time":332.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":329.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it immediately gets to like the call to action point.","index":136,"end_time":335.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":332.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then there''s one that asks more of like an open ended question for the second one if we didn''t get like a response.","index":137,"end_time":348.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":342.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This is something Tristan, one of our owners here recommended is it opens more of a discussion instead of just a link to like an asset that we may not hear anything back from.","index":138,"end_time":358.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":348.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ve got no idea.","index":139,"end_time":362.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":361.71,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Okay, I, I mean I think the, the question on the second email, if you could fix one bottleneck in your current process, what would it be?","index":140,"end_time":372.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":363.47,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I don''t imagine anyone''s going to respond to that.","index":141,"end_time":374.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":372.11,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Like it''s, it''s basically asking you to do some thinking and some work and I just don''t think anyone''s going to respond to that.","index":142,"end_time":380.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":374.91,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I would think having the link, having it to the.","index":143,"end_time":387.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":380.99,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And offering a demo, offering them something is a call to action rather than asking them a question to me seems like a better way to go.","index":144,"end_time":397.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":387.71,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But.","index":145,"end_time":398.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":397.86,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, I know we made a couple of adjustments to the original one here a while back, which we implemented, so we can.","index":146,"end_time":409.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":401.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No one responded to that.","index":147,"end_time":410.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":409.38,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So yeah, these, these have been already implemented like the updates back in July.","index":148,"end_time":415.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":410.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, so we can just.","index":149,"end_time":416.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":416.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If you''re saying you want to still keep it on the demo link, I''ll just restructure the emails and send it over to you guys and see if that''s more what you''re thinking this way.","index":150,"end_time":425.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":416.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We just have so many right now, six in the first bunch is just like an offer without kind of that call to action to book a demo.","index":151,"end_time":434.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":425.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we want to try to prioritize that demo earlier in the messaging sequence.","index":152,"end_time":438.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":434.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if that''s kind of the direction you''d rather take it, where we do have the demo landing page, let me take it back and I''ll create a little bit of adjustments to those other ones that we''re talking about here.","index":153,"end_time":448.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it''s not just an open ended random question, but rather like a specific CTA to the demo.","index":154,"end_time":454.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":448.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Does that sound better?","index":155,"end_time":455.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":454.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s kind of what I''m thinking.","index":156,"end_time":456.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":455.48,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I mean, just really make it as easy and fast and direct as possible.","index":157,"end_time":460.519,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":456.44,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"No one''s going to sit there and muse over these words, you know, like, I don''t know, I don''t know if it''s going to improve the success rate.","index":158,"end_time":468.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":461,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But I mean, from your experience, has this kind of format worked better for your clients or is the let''s book a demo and talk about it kind of thing more effective?","index":159,"end_time":480.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":468.04,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, so when we talked to Tristan, he just mentioned that we need to make it so it''s compelling to the ICP that we''re targeting, like it''ll catch their eye, but also give it a call to action for them to take a step and do something where that''s kind of what we''re lacking right now in the beginning of these sequences where we''re kind of just offering them, like, here''s a video, here''s a link to download this.","index":160,"end_time":499.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":480.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s not prevent, it''s not causing them to have any action to contact you directly for that demo for that call.","index":161,"end_time":505.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":499.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we want to change that.","index":162,"end_time":507.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We want to make that more of a priority in the beginning of the sequence.","index":163,"end_time":510.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":507.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Even better would be an offer like we were talking about, like the beta testing AI idea that you had.","index":164,"end_time":515.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":510.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Something like that will be really catching.","index":165,"end_time":517.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":515.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But until we have that offer, we don''t want to, you know, waste any time with the sequence and kind of just restructure the messaging right now as best we can to kind of increase that engagement.","index":166,"end_time":527.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":517.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I can take that back and I''ll update, I''ll maybe do like three emails kind of around what we''re talking about.","index":167,"end_time":533.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":527.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it''s based on that demo booking.","index":168,"end_time":535.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":533.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then we can even include an introduce Fahad''s calendar thing in the.","index":169,"end_time":540.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":535.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Maybe the third one.","index":170,"end_time":541.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":540.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just so it''s like a direct.","index":171,"end_time":542.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":541.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Here''s my availability if you''d like to book a time.","index":172,"end_time":545.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":543.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m just, I am curious whether something that sounds more personal and direct rather than kind of AI generated might be more effective.","index":173,"end_time":560.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":547.45,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, we can make it more like personable instead of like a, you know, like you''re saying like a robotic kind of sound.","index":174,"end_time":567.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":561.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It sounds like an email campaign.","index":175,"end_time":568.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":567.3,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s.","index":176,"end_time":569.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":568.7,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I mean, this kind of language is very, very typical of a marketing campaign.","index":177,"end_time":573.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":569.02,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And I''m just not sure that that''s landing with our audience.","index":178,"end_time":577.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":573.3,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So I''m thinking something a little more personal.","index":179,"end_time":580.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":578.34,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"On the other hand, the, the super personal approach is what shfahad you guys were taking before and I don''t know if that really worked either.","index":180,"end_time":589,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":580.34,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So I, I just, I don''t know.","index":181,"end_time":590.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":589.08,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I mean honestly the one thing I think we could probably do now that we are ISO certified, I think that should probably be mentioned in the email.","index":182,"end_time":602.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":590.44,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Maybe something about, you know, it''s super direct about making your investigations faster with bank rate security and ISO certified.","index":183,"end_time":615.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":603.48,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"We''d love to give you a demo.","index":184,"end_time":618.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":616.69,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Something really short and direct like that might be better than the salesy kind of marketing language.","index":185,"end_time":623.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":618.29,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But I don''t know Fahad, do you have a sense of that?","index":186,"end_time":626.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":623.93,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I tend to ignore these emails when I get them.","index":187,"end_time":634.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":630.93,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Right.","index":188,"end_time":635.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":634.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You know, I might have requested a demo.","index":189,"end_time":638.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":635.57,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I think Jack, you''ve been a couple of demos where they actually intrigued me and then we see the demo and then there''s nothing really that they''re offering that was worth our time or resources.","index":190,"end_time":653.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":638.53,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So I, I don''t know how these things work.","index":191,"end_time":656.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":653.87,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I know that I promised you guys I''ll send you the one Kate sent out to weil.","index":192,"end_time":660.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":656.75,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It was one out of 400.","index":193,"end_time":662.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":661.07,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I just wrote it down.","index":194,"end_time":663.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":662.55,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''ll send it to you either today or tomorrow.","index":195,"end_time":666.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":663.35,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I do apologize.","index":196,"end_time":667.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":666.31,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I completely forgot that I''ll send that to you.","index":197,"end_time":670.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":667.19,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I don''t remember how she approached them but also she got one response out of 400.","index":198,"end_time":675,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":671,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So it wasn''t that it was a big success rate.","index":199,"end_time":677.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":675.24,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But I''ll have to see how it''s sorted.","index":200,"end_time":681,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":677.8,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"To me you have to when you get an email.","index":201,"end_time":684.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":681.08,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"If I was getting an email, it intrigued me because it is focused on the problem that I''m dealing with and there''s a solution to that problem.","index":202,"end_time":692.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":684.24,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"And you know, this is a SOC 2 type 2 ISO certified organization.","index":203,"end_time":697.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":692.84,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Then maybe it''s worth my time to, you know, spend 30 minutes, see a demo.","index":204,"end_time":702.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":699.07,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But I''ll have to mention right now from all these emails, I don''t see how we''re solving their problem.","index":205,"end_time":710.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":703.55,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"If I was reading this, why would I spend the time.","index":206,"end_time":715.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":711.07,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"How are you reducing the 90% of the time that I have to deal with in onboarding data?","index":207,"end_time":720.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":716.03,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"How are we utilizing the product to simplify your life and giving you investigative advantage over your competition?","index":208,"end_time":728.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":720.59,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I don''t get that from these messages at this stage.","index":209,"end_time":730.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":728.42,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"They''re nice messages but I, I, I don''t, I don''t believe I would respond to any of them.","index":210,"end_time":735.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":731.14,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"And I think we need to, you know, it''s not that we''re getting a lot of responses and I think maybe shift it into this is the problem that you''re dealing with and this is the solution that we have that will fix that problem for you.","index":211,"end_time":750.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":736.58,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"And if it''s not a problem they''re dealing with, they shouldn''t be coming for a demo because there''s nothing we can offer them.","index":212,"end_time":757.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":752.51,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Unless they have issues with that data and that financial investigation element or that procurement, there''s nothing we can offer them.","index":213,"end_time":763.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":757.39,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"You know, you guys have a list of a lot of people right now and not all of them are going to be potential customers, but if we could get 10 out of 10,000 to come back, that''s the 10 possible customers that we''re looking at.","index":214,"end_time":775.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":763.95,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"This first email here, Fahad, where it says many investigation teams still rely on spreadsheets or manual review to piece together complex cases.","index":215,"end_time":784.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":776.38,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It works, but it''s time consuming and often leads to errors and delays.","index":216,"end_time":787.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":784.3,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That seems pretty direct.","index":217,"end_time":788.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":787.1,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Is there some way we can tweak that to be even more to the point?","index":218,"end_time":795.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":790.38,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Like I want to get to the point immediately.","index":219,"end_time":796.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":795.02,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Maybe using numbers, percentages they used to usually stands out.","index":220,"end_time":802.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":797.34,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Reduce the time by 90%, get access to your information within seconds.","index":221,"end_time":807.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":802.22,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Things that, you know, sound surreal but are actually true right now.","index":222,"end_time":812.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":807.87,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Right.","index":223,"end_time":812.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":812.23,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":224,"end_time":815.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":814.91,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, this has seen firms cut their case review time in half, but we, I think throwing out that it''s the 90% reduction in data ingestion time.","index":225,"end_time":826.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":816.83,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Is that it?","index":226,"end_time":826.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":826.11,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I think we could throw that in there.","index":227,"end_time":830.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":827.71,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Okay.","index":228,"end_time":831.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":831.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So actually Taylor, would you send me a link to this again and I will.","index":229,"end_time":835.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":831.99,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I''ll ideate on this a little bit more and see if I can.","index":230,"end_time":838.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":836.11,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I''ve got some of that, those numbers and stuff that we''ve put in else in other places and I''ll just see if we can make that more direct.","index":231,"end_time":845.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":838.91,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":232,"end_time":846.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":845.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And that''s good input too, Fahad.","index":233,"end_time":850.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":846.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like you were saying, from your perspective, what would be best.","index":234,"end_time":852.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":850.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''s kind of what we''re looking for here, is your input for how we can improve it.","index":235,"end_time":856.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":852.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that will be good if we can, like you said.","index":236,"end_time":858.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":856.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":237,"end_time":859.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":858.95,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"And I have something else I forgot.","index":238,"end_time":861.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":859.83,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I think I. I don''t know if it came in last Wednesday or I forgot to mention last Wednesday.","index":239,"end_time":866.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":861.51,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"One of the people that we reached out to through the campaign, the LinkedIn campaign said I''ve heard about you guys from the Mins Group.","index":240,"end_time":877.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":866.55,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It was a firm called from a partner at Boyce Schiller.","index":241,"end_time":881.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":878.15,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s a very large law firm and we have a scheduled to demo with them for tomorrow.","index":242,"end_time":886.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":881.39,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Great.","index":243,"end_time":887.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":886.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I also included the people that have mentioned us to him and on that call.","index":244,"end_time":892.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":888.04,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So that''s taking place tomorrow.","index":245,"end_time":894.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":892.52,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"This way we get the Mince group, which is a friendly face that they know, and us to see the demo tomorrow.","index":246,"end_time":900.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":894.36,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":247,"end_time":902.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":901.96,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So the, you know, we''re getting something.","index":248,"end_time":905,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":902.32,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s not that we''re not getting anything, but we need to pick it up a little bit to get to where we need to be.","index":249,"end_time":912.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":905,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":250,"end_time":913.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":913.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s great to hear.","index":251,"end_time":914.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":913.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thanks for sharing that.","index":252,"end_time":915.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":914.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And yeah, we definitely want to refine the messaging here and make it more clear to your icp.","index":253,"end_time":920.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":915.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, yes, I will send that link over to you, Jackie, and we can adjustments and just fahad.","index":254,"end_time":927.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":920.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, you know, this is often how things go.","index":255,"end_time":929.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":927.34,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Like, you chum the waters with marketing for like nine months until you finally start hearing things from people and they''re like, oh, yeah, I''ve heard of you.","index":256,"end_time":935.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":929.02,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s like they''ve been.","index":257,"end_time":936.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":935.34,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Because you''ve gotten in front of them for like 12 times or whatever, and then they remember you.","index":258,"end_time":941.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":936.34,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"They''re like, all right.","index":259,"end_time":942.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":941.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"To be honest, I wish.","index":260,"end_time":945.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":944.4,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''m not saying that that''s not the.","index":261,"end_time":947.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":946.32,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"The reason he accepted the connection, but I.","index":262,"end_time":950.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":947.92,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It was mainly because this lady, her name is Jen, out of the D.C. office of Men''s group, was talking to him, trying to tell them about their capabilities and how they utilize the resolutions in financial investigation, so on and so forth.","index":263,"end_time":963.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":950.56,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So he actually heard it from another colleague in person.","index":264,"end_time":968.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":963.84,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"And then when he got the request, he''s like, oh, I know these guys, you know, so it''s good, you know, but word of mouth is very important.","index":265,"end_time":978.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":968.93,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"That''s why getting these projects in is quite important as well.","index":266,"end_time":982.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":979.25,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"What we''re doing is good for branding, for recognition, hopefully long term.","index":267,"end_time":986.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":982.69,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But, yeah, there''s a lot of trial and error, obviously.","index":268,"end_time":990.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":987.97,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve been at it for a while, so I get that.","index":269,"end_time":992.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":990.93,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":270,"end_time":994.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":994.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Great.","index":271,"end_time":996.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":995.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So one more thing I want to review during our meeting is I know we''ve been going back and forth about paid ads and there''s a lot on the screen here, so I want to break it down, but I want to make sure that the money that you guys are giving for the budget to these ads is being beneficial to you.","index":272,"end_time":1010.179,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":997.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And if it''s not, we don''t want to keep doing that.","index":273,"end_time":1012.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1010.179,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So something that I''ve noticed is the Google Ads, we haven''t seen a ton of success there.","index":274,"end_time":1016.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1012.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We have seen a little bit more leads come through with forensic accounting software is our main keyword because we didn''t want to keep wasting it on Things that we weren''t populating for.","index":275,"end_time":1027.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1017.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But this is still a very broad keyword.","index":276,"end_time":1030.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1027.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This is kind of like a general fraud detection term.","index":277,"end_time":1033.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1030.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it wasn''t aligning closely with CEDRA specifically.","index":278,"end_time":1036.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1033.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I asked our paid media specialist to go through and kind of like give me a broad data overview of what''s going on.","index":279,"end_time":1041.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1036.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So she''s recommending that right now we maybe turn off Google Ads, the budget and reallocate it into LinkedIn.","index":280,"end_time":1050.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1043.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The reason for this is because LinkedIn is doing really good with delivering about nine leads average per month.","index":281,"end_time":1056.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1050.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As you can see in those spreadsheets that I send with those lead generation ads, we have people giving their data with their emails, their names.","index":282,"end_time":1063.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1056.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And these leads are more top of funnel because they''re giving us that info in exchange for those guides that we''re offering.","index":283,"end_time":1071.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1064.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So our idea is if we do reallocate the budget out of Google Ads, we pause those for now, put that additional 1500 into LinkedIn, we would create a website conversion campaign that would directly bring those users to the demo landing page.","index":284,"end_time":1087.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1072.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This has been better for like lowering the cost per lead as well so that we can get more kind of the bang for the buck instead of just wasting it and it gives more higher relevance.","index":285,"end_time":1099.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1088.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We also want to make sure that we''re getting the leads that we were putting the money in for.","index":286,"end_time":1105.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1099.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if we take the money out of Google Ads, we can put more behind LinkedIn and then create a new campaign with that additional budget to target people to the demo landing page.","index":287,"end_time":1114.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1105.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then later on down the line, once we start seeing more success with that and data come through, we can create a retargeting Google Ad search campaign.","index":288,"end_time":1122.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1114.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that way we can use the data that we''ve seen with the people that didn''t end up converting into Google Ads.","index":289,"end_time":1128.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1123.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then in the future we can talk more about specifics of Google Ads that we could run based on that data.","index":290,"end_time":1135.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1129.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But right now, with the money that you''re putting in monthly, we''re not seeing a great return.","index":291,"end_time":1139.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1135.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we don''t want you to keep using that money if it''s not being beneficial.","index":292,"end_time":1143.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1139.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So to kind of break it down a little bit more.","index":293,"end_time":1145.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1143.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Right now just paid Media, we have 1500 in Google Analytics and 1500 and LinkedIn.","index":294,"end_time":1150.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1145.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we would just recommend, like I said, reallocating that budget to 3,000 total for LinkedIn of just paid.","index":295,"end_time":1156.739,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1151.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This doesn''t include ABM ads.","index":296,"end_time":1158.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1157.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll get to that secondary.","index":297,"end_time":1159.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1158.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But what do you think about that idea?","index":298,"end_time":1161.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1159.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Does that sound good?","index":299,"end_time":1164.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1163.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, we just want to make sure your money''s being used, you know, the well to create those leads.","index":300,"end_time":1171.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1164.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And right now we''re not seeing that return on Google Ads.","index":301,"end_time":1174.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1171.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We figured we could do better on LinkedIn since we see good progress there.","index":302,"end_time":1178.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1174.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Sure did we talk about though redirecting some of that to make sure we''re ranking number one for Cedra.","index":303,"end_time":1185.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1179.05,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, Cedra is still the one that we, we have is like that one prioritized.","index":304,"end_time":1191.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1186.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But for those additional keywords that we were talking about, we had originally a longer list if you remember.","index":305,"end_time":1196.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1191.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Then we kind of adjusted it and now we just don''t think it''s, it''s as beneficial as what we see coming through LinkedIn.","index":306,"end_time":1203.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1196.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we go ahead and do that, set up that new campaign and then we''ll monitor that each week and I''ll share those statistics with you in our weekly meetings so we can keep a close eye on that.","index":307,"end_time":1212.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1204.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":308,"end_time":1213.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1212.59,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Great.","index":309,"end_time":1214.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1214.11,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then just wanted to give you an update on ABM ads.","index":310,"end_time":1217.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1214.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Those are still doing well.","index":311,"end_time":1218.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1217.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We have the 1500 on LinkedIn and then the 500 on AdRoll.","index":312,"end_time":1221.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1218.19,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The click volume so far in November has risen to 14 clicks on AdRoll, which is great.","index":313,"end_time":1227.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1222.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The two best ones are the financial investigative solutions ad and the case study ad that we have.","index":314,"end_time":1233.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1227.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We also lowered the cost per click which is always good to see.","index":315,"end_time":1236.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1233.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we keep an eye on those.","index":316,"end_time":1238.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1237.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then for LinkedIn we''ve seen strong engagement as well with 19 clicks already in November.","index":317,"end_time":1244.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1239.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Our paid media specialist, each week she goes through and she shifts budget around to put more money behind the best performing ads.","index":318,"end_time":1252.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1245.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so something to you did notice is I just wanted to share is a lot of impressions are coming from these particular levels of partners, associates and founders in the major metro areas.","index":319,"end_time":1263.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1252.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So these are the main ones that we''re seeing but we have that long list I know that we continue to add to but these are just the main ones that have the most engagement.","index":320,"end_time":1271.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1263.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''s good to see as well.","index":321,"end_time":1273.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1272.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we will, we will continue to keep an eye on everything but I wanted to make sure that what we have running on everything is, is giving us a good return.","index":322,"end_time":1284.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1275.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so we''ve been keeping an eye on Google Ads and we kind of figure now might be a good time to switch it up.","index":323,"end_time":1289.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1284.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''ll closely monitor that, create that new campaign and hopefully direct more people straight to the demo landing page and yeah, but I will keep you guys updated each week with some stats for that.","index":324,"end_time":1302.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1289.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":325,"end_time":1304.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1303.68,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":326,"end_time":1305.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1304.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll go ahead and send that sequence over to you Jackie.","index":327,"end_time":1308,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1305.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And yeah, Sounds good.","index":328,"end_time":1310.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1308,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you, everybody.","index":329,"end_time":1310.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1310.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Have a good rest of your day.","index":330,"end_time":1311.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1310.92,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Bye.","index":331,"end_time":1312.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1311.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"}],"dateString":"2025-11-12T16:30:00.000Z","host_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88927304763?pwd=asbbQolEtVpMuYX5uccJpOibhnlog1.1","participants":["taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com,baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com,j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com,i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com,f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com","baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com","i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com","f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01K9QBWARH87KQ8QGDMCSXHAD5","organizer_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.88,"bullets":["Resolved Arabic caption mismatch on video project to finalize edit for delivery.","Agreed to prioritize clearer demo CTAs in email sequence to increase response rate.","Shifted $1,500 ad budget from Google to LinkedIn to optimize cost per lead generation.","Aligned on strategy to emphasize ISO certification and reduce time claims in outreach.","Confirmed new lead from Boies Schiller via partner referral with demo scheduled tomorrow."],"highlights":[{"quote":"To me you have to when you get an email… it is focused on the problem that I''m dealing with and there''s a solution to that problem.","speaker":"fahad al mutawa"},{"quote":"We would create a website conversion campaign that would directly bring those users to the demo landing page.","speaker":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"quote":"So the, you know, we''re getting something. It''s not that we''re not getting anything, but we need to pick it up a little bit to get to where we need to be.","speaker":"fahad al mutawa"}],"topics":["email","ads","demo","outreach","lead_generation"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-11-13T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
