lprits worldwide.","index":288,"end_time":832.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":827.34,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah, I think that works.","index":289,"end_time":833.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":832.66,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I like the text that we use today and that in one of the LinkedIn posts Kai can remember, it mentions that building web and app integrating and creating one solid experience, then that should be part of the message.","index":290,"end_time":854.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":833.78,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Do you remember?","index":291,"end_time":855.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":854.78,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Do you know what I''M talking about guy.","index":292,"end_time":856.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":855.46,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I think I am talking about the Foxes one.","index":293,"end_time":862.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":856.78,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yes, you''re right.","index":294,"end_time":863.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":862.46,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"It''s not the same one.","index":295,"end_time":864.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":863.66,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"No, it would have been if we built the app or the web for St. Andrew.","index":296,"end_time":870.7,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":867.34,"speaker_name":"Kylee Anger"},{"text":"Correct?","index":297,"end_time":871.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":870.94,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we did not.","index":298,"end_time":871.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":871.26,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"But no, we.","index":299,"end_time":872.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":871.94,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"It mentions in Tom''s post in.","index":300,"end_time":876.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":872.62,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"He mentions the partnership and also mentions the user experienc